Unikezo lwesibonelelo sezempilo
ISebe lezoThutho neMisebenzi yoLuntu leNtshona Koloni lihambisa izibonelelo
neenkonzo ebantwini bephondo ukukhuthaza iziphumo zoqoqosho nentlalo-
ntle nezikhuselekileyo, ezixhotyisiweyo nezimanyeneyo.
Ubonisa inkqubela umsebenzi weSebe lezoThutho neMisebenzi yoLuntu kwiphulo lalo lokubuyisela isidima sesibhedlele sembali iValkenberg Hospital
e-Observatory, eKapa. Sakha amagumbi oogqirha nawonyango kunye nawabalawuli besibhedlele.
Le projekthi imanqanaba mabini ixabisa imali ezizigidi
ezili-R146, yaqala kweyoKwindla 2014 yaye sijonge ukuba igqitywe kweyoKwindla 2017.
Sithetha nje sakhiwa ngokutsha iSibhedlele saseValkenberg yaye ngoku siza kuba neendawo ezintsha zokuhlala izigulane ezifuna ukuqwalaselisiswa
nezimeko yazo inzulu naqatha.
Isibhedlele esi simi phezu komhlaba oziihekthare ezingama-29 phakathi kwemilambo emibini ebizwa ngokuba yiLiesbeek River neBlack River.
Sinembali eyodwa ebalulekileyo nendima exabisekileyo kwezenkcubeko ngenxa yokuba kwakulo mhlaba kukho isibhedlele
sengqondo esema apho kuwo kwangeminyaka yoo-1890.
ISebe lizinikele ekuboneleleni amathuba omsebenzi ngeNkqubo yeMisebenzi yoLuntu eNatyisiweyo (EPWP) kunye nokuphuhlisa amashishini okwakha
asakhasayo.
Zonke iithagethi zomsebenzi kwikhontrakhthi yeNqanaba 1 ziphunyezwe ngemali engangezigidi ezilishumi zeerandi (R10m) ezichithwe
kumashishini abe ethagethiwe ukuza kuthi ga ngoku.
Ukongeza apho, abaxhamli abangama-29 baye banikwa uqeqesho lobugcisa kwezobuchweli.
Sihamba phambili ekuhanjisweni kwezibonelelo zikarhulumente kunye neenkonzo ezinxulumene noko.
