Ukubekwa kweliso kumsebenzi
kubandakanya ingqinisekiso yokuLinga, eyindlela ebanzi yokubekwa kweliso okuthi ngokunjalo kunike ithuba iiNPO lokwenza uvavanyo lwazo.
Amagosa okubekwa kweliso nocvaanyo angama-40 (ali-15 amatsha nama-25 ekudala ekho) aqeqeshwa kwisiCwangciso-nkqubo
seNgqinisekiso yokuLunga.
I SOP elungiselelwe ii-odolo zoKwandiswa kwamaZiko oLolongo loMntwana noLutsha yaphuhliswa yamkelwa ngoMatshi 2017.
IsiCwagciso sePhondo soLawulo loLolongo lobuMpelesi samkelwa ngoMatshi wama-2017.
Ulwakhiwo lwamakhono kwizithethe nemigangatho kunye nenkqubo ephuculweyo yokubekwa kweliso nokunikwa kwengxelo kube
nomphumela kuhambelwano olwandisiweyo lweNPO.
I SOP eyilwayo ngokususwa kwaBantwana basiwe kuLolongo oluKhuselekileyo kweThutyana yaphuhliswa kunyaka wokunikwa kwengxelo
yaye ilindele ulwamkelo lokugqibela
Iqhinga lokucwangcisa amagumbi okusebenzela aneenkqubo kunye nezithili zokuvavanya ukusebenza kwenkqubo ze kwenziwe izigqibo
zeqhinga malunga nekujoliswe kuko okuhlaziyiweyo nokubekwa phambili kokunikezelwa kwenkonzo.
