ISebe libeke phambili ukuqinisekiswa kwabaqeshwa ngeenjongo zokhuseleko yaye licele i-
arhente kaRhulumente yoKhuseleko ukuqukumbela inkqubo yoqinisekiso lwabaqeshwa
kwisithuba esifutshane ukugcina iimfuno zohambelwano.
Amalungu eKomiti yoKhuseleko azimase uqeqesho lokhuseleko olwamkelekileyo olunikezelwa
nguMphathiswa woLawulo loShishino loKhuseleko lwaNgasese (PSIRA) ze yafumana igreyidingi
E  A. IKomiti sele iyivavanyile yayisayina yonke imigaqo-nkqubo enxulumene nokhuselo
nokhuseleko ukulungiselela umiliselo.
