ifumana
isikhokelo kwimiba ephambili yomgaqo-nkqubo wephondo
neenjongo ezicwangcisiweyo, kwimiba ephambili yomgaqo-nkqubo wesizwe,
kwiimfuno zemithetho yesizwe neemfuno zemithetho yephondo kwaye
inika
ingqalelo kwiinkcukacha zobalo lwakutsha-nje kwiimfuno zentlalo nezoqoqosho
notshintsho kwiphondo.
Le miba iphambili iyaqhubeka ngokusebenzisana kwaye kufuneka isetyenziswe
kunye ukuxhasa injongo enye, endaweni yokuba kukhutshiswane ngayo ukuyiphumeza.
Siliphondo, siza
zinto zifanelekileyo nezipngxamisekileyo ngokweemfuno nangokweemeko
zentlalo nezoqoqosho kubantu abahlala eNtshona Koloni.
ISebe loPhuhliso loLuntu (DSD) liye lahambelana neziphumo neenjongo zizonke
zesiCwangciso soPhuhliso seSizwe (NDP).
I-NDP iqwalasela ekunciphiseni intlupheko
nokungalingani kwaye iqwalasele imiba emininzi yongenelelo.
Iinjongo neziphumo
zizonke zeNDP zihambelana ngqo neNjongo ecwangcisiweyo yePhondo (PSO) 8:
umz. Ukwandisa ukubandakanywa koluntu nokuncitshiswa kwentlupheko. I-NDP
ithetha ngeendawo ezingavaniyo nemfuneko yokhuseleko lweNtlalo (Isahluko 11),
kunye nokutshintsha uLuntu nokuManya iLizwe (Isahluko 15) kunye nokuphucula
iMfundo, uQeqesho noTshintsho (Isahluko 9). I-PSO8
ilandelayo esengqondweni: ingaba lo ngowona mgaqo-nkqubo yeyona ndlela
yokukhuthaza ukubandakanyeka koluntu ngendlela ezinzileyo nokunciphisa
intlupheko kwabo baxhamlayo kujoliswe kubo?
Le njongo iquka le miba ilandelayo iphambili:
