iv  Ukuthintela nokunciphisa ubundlobongela
Ukwandisa ukuthatha inxaxheba kwiimeko zentlalo
Ndizimisele ukwandisa amathuba okuphuhlisa ulutsha, ukuqinisekisa ukuba iinkqubo
zabemi zizinzile, kwaye zinegalelo elibalulekileyo kubomi babo, ingakumbi malunga
nokuncitshiswa kwentswela-ngqesho kulutsha.
Ukuza kuma ngoku, isicwangciso
sethu esitsha sokuphuhliswa kolutsha sifuna ukunceda abantu abatsha ukuba
bakwazi ukuzimela baziphelele bazinze kwezoqoqosho, babesempilweni
babenonxibelelwano oluphilileyo boa, iintsapho zabo noluntu, kwaye kufuneka
Ukulandelela ezi ziphumo aabantu
abatsha isicwangciso sifumanisa uluhlu olubanzi lweenkonzo, lweenkqubo kuxhaswa
neenkqubo eziza kuqinisekisa ukuba bayakwazi ukufumana amathuba
abawadingayo ukuze baphuhle.
Ngapha koko, sihleli siqwalasela ekwandiseni umgangatho wee-ECD, apho iinkqubo
zokufunda ezichazwe ngokucacileyo ziye ziphunyezwe, kubantwana abaninzi.
kwabo bancinci, ukubaphuhlisa
ngokwentlalo, ngokwasengqondweni anngokwasemzimbeni yeyona nto siyibeka
phambili urhulumente anokuyenza enokuqhubela phambili ukubandakanya uluntu
nokunciphisa intlupheko.
Usapho, ukukhathalelwa kwabantwana ukuphuhliswa
esizicingayo. Sihleli
sinomngeni wokulwa ubundlobongela kwiindawo zethu, ingakumbi
ukujongana nemiba ekhoyo yentlalo ebangela ubundlobongela.
Iinkqubo zethu
zongenelelo ukwenza kubekho amanye amathuba abantu abatsha, ngendlela
ebavumela babenamandla okwenza izinto ezilungileyo, ziza kuqhubeka.
Ukunciphisa umonakalo onxulumene neziyobisi notywala kwiphondo yinto ephambili
hayi kuphela kweli phondo, kodwa kuRhulumente weNtshona Koloni.
Siqwalasela
ubungakanani bomngeni kwaye
sizimisele ukusebenzisa izibonelelo esinazo
ukuqinisekisa ukuba oko kuza kuba neempembelelo ezimandla kubomi babo bazidinga kakhulu iinkonzo. v
Siza kuqhubeka ukwandisa iinkonzo zokuXhotyiswa kwamaXhoba ukuze sikwazi
ukufikelela kwababhinqileyo nabantwana abaninzi ababuthathaka abadinga
ukukhathalelwa nenkxaso ukulwa iingxaki abanazo. Ngokokuphuculwa kophuhliso lwesebe,
ukuchaneka
nokuba luncedo
zengxelo kuhleli
kuphambili kwisebe.
ezinikezela iinkonzo ekuhlaleni ezingama-34 ngumngeni omkhulu wesebe njengoko ubonisiwe kwiingxelo zonyaka zangaphambili.
Noxa
kunjalo, kubalulekile
ukuqinisekisa ukuba iimali zikarhulumente ezisetyenziswe kwezi nkonzo zibonelela
okuzuzwayo okuphambili kusenzelwa uluntu oluhlelelekileyo nolubuthathaka
lwaseNtshona Koloni.
Okokugqibela, le APP ifumana isikhokelo kwiChildrens Act, iChild Justice Act ne-
Older Persons Act, kunye neProvincial Education Act, yonke ineempembelelo kwizibonelelo zeDSD. Ukuphendula kubuninzi bemingeni
yezentlalo
lethu elikhula ngokukhawuleza, iza kuhlala ingumsebenzi ongaphaya.
Uza kufuna sisebenzisane
ngokupheleleyo ukuya phambili, kwaye ndiyathemba ukuba le APP exhaswa yiPSO8
iza kuqinisekisa ukuba izinto zethu eziphambili ziyalingana, zinenkqubela kwaye
zineempembelelo ezibalulekileyo kubantu esibasebenzelayo.
