#BoozeFreeRoads
abomvu ukuthatha ikhefu yaye luza kube luphuma neentsapho nezihlobo lusiya kwiindawo
ngeendawo zokuphola kulo eli lethu lihle ngokuncamisayo, bambi bephumela nangaphandle kwalo.
Kambe eli xesha likwaqapheleka
nangokuba abantu babusela kakhulu utywala yaye neziyobisi bazisebenzisa ngokugqithisileyo,
abanye ke besenziwa yimincili xa bebhiyoza ngelixa, ngelishwa, abanye besela kuba bebaleka
iinzingo zangeli xesha linye, bekhumbula nezithandwa zabo ezabashiyayo nezinye
izithwakumbe.
Kubalulekile ke ngoko ukuba sizikhumbuze ngeengozi zeendlela.
Ngenxa
yeenzame zecandelo leeNkonzo zezeNdlela zePhondo kunye namahlakani
ethu kwezolawulo lweendlela, iinkonzo zezempilo nezemfundo lehlile
inani labantu abalishiyayo eli ngenxa yeengozi zendlela ngexesha
leeholide zehlobo.
Kanti nangona kunjalo, bangama--640 bebonke
abantu abalishiyileyo eli ngexesha leeholide zehlobo zenyanga yoMnga-
ngeli xesha lonyaka kunye nentlungu eviwa ziintsapho nezihlobo zamaxhoba
kungumthwalo onzima nanjengokuba kulusizi ukubona amaxhoba xa engxwelerhekile.
Xa siwajongile la manani uyabona ukuba sikho esi sandla
luluntu.
Amapolisa athi kubea kufuneka eye kuninka ingqwalasela kuloo ndawo
yexhwayelo, babe abaphuli-mthetho behlasela kwelinye icala, amagumbi eengxwelerha
namacandelo abenzakele kakhulu athi exakeke kukujonga amaxhoba eengozi kufuneke
