IMBULAMBETHE
Esi siCwangciso soMsebenzi soNyaka sijolise ekubeni sisebenze ngokusondeleyo kumbono wethu
weNtshona Koloni equkayo ezentlalo, enobuchule nekwaziyo ukuyila.
Iinjongo zayo kukudalela abantu bethu amathuba, ingakumbi ulutsha, ukuthabatha inxaxheba emidlalweni,
kwezolonwabo, ubugcisa nenkcubeko nokuphucula indlela yokufikelela kumathala ethu eencwadi, iimyuziyam nakwiinkonzo zelifa lemveli.
Ukwandisa imali esinayo kubonisa iqondo eliphakamileyo lengqiniseko esinayo kulawulo lweli Sebe
ukuze sibanike iinkonzo ezisemgangathweni abantu beNtshona Koloni.
Ezona ntsika ziphambili
zentembeko, uxanduva lokuphendula, ubuchule nolwazi, ukukhawulelana neemeko nokunika inkathelo njengento elandelwayo kuzo zonke iinkqubo.
Sikholelwa ekubeni oku kuya kungena kuzo zonke iinkqubo zethu xa sikwenza oko ngokolawulo olufanelekileyo lwequmrhu.
Okona kubaluleke kakhulu kukwanda kwemali ebekelwe bucala yeNkonzo yeThala leencwadi
kunye neNkqubo ye-MOD (Mass participation; Opportunity and Access; Development and growth).
INkonzo yeThala leencwadi lidlala indima ebaluleke kakhulu ekuxhotyisweni komntu
wonke, omdala nomcinane ngokufanayo.
Inkonzo ephakamileyo yethala leencwadi iya kwenza
uluntu luzive lunebango negugu.
Kananjalo likwanika abantu bethu kwiinkolo ezahlukeneyo
zephondo ukuba bafikelele kwiqondo lokuba ngabo
INkqubo ye-MOD yeyona nto kulula ukuyisebenzisa ngenxa yokuba ivumelana maxa onke
namaphulo ophuhliso lolutsha. IsiCwangciso soMsebenzi soNyaka sijoliswe ekuphakamiseni
kwiNtshona Koloni.
Athatyathiwe amanyathelo ngokolawulo olufnalekileyo nobeko-liso
ukuqinisekisa ukuba amaZiko ee-MOD aya ephucuka ngokuphucuka.
Ngokwenza njalo, iSebe
lilindele ukuba likwazi ukurhwebesha inani elikhulu labafundi libe semidlalweni, kwinkqubo
yezobugcisa nenkcubeko esemva kwexesha lesikolo eyenziwa kula maziko.
IsiCwangciso soMsebenzi soNyaka sibonakalisa ukuba iSebe eli liya kuba nako ukuphumeza iinjongo zalo ngokwentsebenziswano efanelekileyo.
Ngokuxhobisa iimanyano zezemidlalo
kwakunye nemibutho yezenkcubeko ibalulekile nayo. La maziko asoloko eyindawo enkulu
yemibutho yemidlalo neyenkcubeko esebenzisana neSebe ukuxhobisa imibutho emincinane,
engekabinamava.
