ISishwankathelo sesiCwangciso soPhuliso 2030 (NDP) sicacisa ukuba ubugcisa nenkcubeko
sinethuba elinamandla lokukubonisana apho isosayethi imile kwaye isazi nalapho iya khona
(iphepha lama-26).
Yakhuthazwa ngokufanelekileyo, inkqubo yokuyila nemisebenzi yezenkcubeko inganegalelo kumashishini asakhukayo, ukudlala mathuba omsebenzi nophuhliso ndawonye
nokuhlaziywa kommandla wedolophu.
elityebileyo leli lizwe nobuchule bokuyila babantu balo kuthetha ukuba uMzantsi Afrika ungeza
namabali obaluleke ngokukodwa, amazwi nemveliso eya kuya ezizweni zehlabathi.
Ukongeza
koku, amalinge obugcisa nendlela yokwandla umcimbi ungeza nezinto ezisemgangathweni
usebenzele ukuba uphilise kananjalo ubuyisele ukuzingca kwesizwe.Oku kubhekiselela ngqo
kwindima edlalwa yiDCAS inegalelo lokuhlanganisa wonkumntu, ukwakha isizwe nokuqinisa ubunye ezentlalo kuzwelonke.
I-NDP icingela ukuba uluntu kufuneka lukhuthaze ubunye eluntwini.
Ngokumayela noku, imibutho emininzi engenzi nzuzo (NGOS) kunye nemibutho yoluntu (CBOs) idlala indima enkulu kwezentlalo nakwezengqesho.
Isishwankathelo seNDP sikwaphakamisa ukuba:
ukwenziwa nokunatyiswa kwazo zonke iintlobo zobugcisa kufuneka udale impiliso nolwakhiwo
lwesizwe; ingxoxo equlathe isibonelelo senkuthazo esenzelwe ukukhuthaza ubunye nolwakhiwo
lwesizwe ( iphepha 66). Njengoko kwenziwe iziphakamiso kwindawo, uwiso-mthethi iDCAS esebenza ngalo Lunika
amathuba kubemi ukuba bathathe inxaxheba kuburhulumente bengavoti nje kuphela (iphepha 27).
EDCAS ezi foram zolawulo loburhulumente ziquka amaBhunga neeKomiti zeLifa leMveli
leNtshona Koloni, iKomishini yobuGcisa yeNtshona Koloni, iKomiti yeeLwimi yeNtshona Koloni,
amaqumrhu alawulayo eemyuziyam neqela elininzi lemibutho elawulayo.
La maqumrhu alilizwi loluntu kwakunye namathuba okulungisa amaziko akufutshane nalo.
Esinye seziphakamiso (zeNDP isishwankathelo sesiGqeba iphepha 27) kukuba isizwe sixhase sijule
esivivaneni kumalinge oluntu.
