Ukuzinikela ekuphuculeni ilungelo lokufikelela kwiziko lezolondolozo-maxwebhu loRhulumente
weNtshona Koloni ngokobuxhakaxhaka bekhompyutha kuya kuhlala kuqhubeka.Oku kuya
kubandakanya ukuzinikela ekusebenziseni uhlobo lokufayilisha ekuthiwa yi e-filing, kwanokwenziwa kwezinto ngokweedijithi ndawonye neerekhodi zembali.
Liya kuthi lakuba lifumene iskena
esisebenisa iidijithi, iZiko loLondolozo lwamaxwebhu eembali eziBalulekileyo neeRekhodi leNtshona
Koloni limisele inkqubo yephulo lokwenza afumaneke loo maxwebhu/rekhodi ngekhompyutha.
Oku kujongwe ukuba kuphucule uziso lweenkonzo kwaye kuya kukhawulelana kakuhle nezicelo
zabaxhamli-nkonzo abafuna iirekhodi ekhompyutheni. INkonzo yooVimba iya kuqhubeka ukuzisa iinkonzo zolawulo lwamaqumrhu oRhulumente eNtshona
Koloni, oko kusenziwa ngokuhambelana nogunyaziso lomthetho ukwenza urhulumente asebenze
ngokufanelekileyo.
Le misebenzi ilandelayo yobeko-liso yenziwa qho ngonyaka: uhlolo lweerekhodi
neesistim; ukuqeqeshwa kwabalawula iirekhodi; ukuhlolwa nokuvunywa kweerekhodi
ngokwamanqam namaqondo; ukukhutshwa kwamagunya okushenxisa/okususa; nommiselo
wokunceda iingcali ngokubanzi. INkonzo yooVimba yeNtshona Koloni igcina uthelelwano lwentsebenziswano kunye namaziko
anakho ukuyinceda ukufezekisa iinjongo zayo.Iirekhodi zooVimba zifakwa kwikhompyutha
ngothelelwano neGenealogical Society of Utah, yaseUSA.
Izinto ezibalolekileyo ezatshintshayo kulawulo loovimba mpepha neerekhodi kukubalula into
efunekayo kwizilungiso lomthetho iProvincial Archives and Records Service of the Western Cape
