Enye yezinto ezingundoqo kule Nkonzo kukugcina iirekhodi ezibalulekileyo.
Xa sithetha gabalala,
yavuyelwainkqubo eyagqithiselwa kooVimba bempepha ezibalulekilkeyo neerekhodi ukuba ibe
nguye ozilondolozayo kwiZiko loLondolozo, kananjalo nokusebenza ngeerekhodi ezo ndawonye
nokufaka iinkcukacha kwikhompyutha ukuze kukwazeke ukufumaneka kolwazi olukwezi rekhodi.
Eyona nto ngathi iyingxakana yeyokuba ukugcinwa kwentetho kwenziwa ngeendlela eziliqela
ezahlukeneyo ezifuna ukuqwalaselwa ngokumayela neemeko zeerekhodi ezo eziye zisetyenziswe
Ukutsala abantu abaninzi bakwazi ukufikelela kule mbalasane yembali yethu kwanokuba nezizayo
izizukulwana zikwazi ukufikelela kuyo, iinkqubo ezisiwa eluntwini kuya kuhlala kuqhubeka
bolondolozo-mbali.
Kuya kube kujongwe kulutsha, ingakumbi abafundi nezityudenti.
Imidlalo noLonwabo
NgoJanuwari nangoFebruwari wama-2013, iintlanganiso eziqamleze kathathu zahlala ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuba zasetyenziswa njani na iigranti eziyimali.
Ezi ntlanganiso zintlantlu-ntathu
zezeeseshini zobeko-liso novavanyo phakathi kweDCAS, amabhunga emidlalo (amale uluntu)
kunye neemanyano zezemidlalo (ezingabaxhamli kwiigranti eziyimali).
Ngeso sizathu, iMidlalo
noLonwabo yaba nakho ukuqalisa ngeenkqubo ezintsha ezithi zincedise kukhutshelo ukuba
lwenzeke kwangethuba kuneminyaka engaphezulu, kunceda nayiphi na imbumba efanelekileyo
ukuba iqalise ngokumilisela inkqubo yayo ngokukhawuleza kakhulu
Inkqubo ye-MOD ihleli iyintsika yeli phulo lokukhuthaza ulutsha oluhamba isikolo ukuba
luzibandakanye eemidlalweni nakwezelonwabo.
Le nkqubo inenjongo ethile yokukhuthaza ulutsha
ukuba luzibandakanye kwiinkqubo ezakhayo ngokulunika amathuba aqulunqwe ngendlela ethile ukuze lube nokuzijula kuwo emva kwesikolo.
Oku kuya kunciphisa ubungozi bokuba abantu
abatsha benze izinto ezingokhiyo nezinobungozi njengokusebenzisa iziyobisi ngelizonwabisayo
nezimilo ezingamkelekanga.
Le Nkqubo yeMOD iyinkqubo yokuphuhlisa izakhono, ikwaphanda
nezakhono olunazo ulutsha lulunike namathuba okuthatha inxaxheba emidlalweni ekwinqanaba
eliphezulu.Ukwangeza koku ikwadale namathuba emisebenzi eminizi yabaqeqeshi nabalawuli bemidlalo ababandakanyekayo kule nkqubo.
Inkxaso-mali ye-General Budget Support (IGBS) ekwisigidi esingama-R36 ifakiwe kwinkqubo yeMOD
ukuze ibe yipeojekthi ezimeleyo.
Kwangezwe imali yesibonelelo ejolise ekuqasheni abalawuli
abakumgangatho ophakathi.
Iprojekthi yeMOD iphinde yanikwa isixamali esizizigidi ezingama-R2
ukwenzela iprojekthi {eyi-gapejolise ekuxhaseni izakhono zezifundo zemathematiki, inzululwazi
nobuchwepheshe. Abafundi abakwinqubo yeMOD ababonisa ukuba banawo amandla okwenza kwanokuba
