imidlalo ezikolweni ukuba ishenxile kwinto ebekusoloko kujoliswe kuyo ukusuka kwinkqubo
yokulandela inkqubo enye yemidlalo kunye nohlobo lomdlalo ochaphazelekayo wequmrhu
simisela i-WCED ukuba ibe noxanduva lweleague yemidlalo ephakathi kwezikolo kwaye yona i-
DCAS inoxanduva lokujongana namaqela ommandla wawephondo.
Bamenywa abafundi ukuba babekho kwiMidlalo yeZikolo eyayiseNtshona Koloni emva yokuba
bethe bachongwa njengeembaleki ezithembisayo ngexesha leenkqubo zaseSharp Centre,
ukhuphiswano lwemidlalo yezikolo zezithili kunye nemidlalo yeemanyano zemidlalo zezithili.
IiSharp
Centres zijonge ukwenza amathuba aphakamileyo omsebenzi kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa
nenkcubeko nolonwabo kwabo bafundi banezakhono kumaziko eeMOD.
