Inkqutyana 3.3: Ulondolozo lweeNkcukacha eziBalulekileyo
Imilinganiselo yokuphuculwa komgangatho icwangciswe ngoluhlobo lulandelayo ngabeenkonzo
zoLondolozo lweeNkcukacha eziBalulkileyo kunyaka-mali we-2014/15.
Ukuze komelezwe izakhono zokulawulwa kwamaxwebhu kumaqumrhu karhulumente,
kuyimfuneko ukuqinisekisa ukuphunyezwa kwezona nkqubo zilungileyo zokwahlulwa kwamaxwebhu.
Izifundo zoqeqesho ziza kwenziwa kubasebenzi abalawula amaxwebhu
kumaqumrhu karhulumente ukuphucula ulawulo lwamaxwebhu oluntu, ukuze
kuphunyezwe iinkqubo ezisebenzayo zokulondolozwa kwamaxwebhu kumaqumrhu
karhulumente, amaxwebhu anexabiso akuchongwa kwangaphambili ukuqinisekisa ukuba
adluliselwa kwindawo yogcino lweenkcukacha ngexesha elifanelekileyo.
Iprojekthi yokuPhumeza i-WCG Transversal ECM (Enterprise Content Management) yaqalwa
kunyaka-mali yowe-2013/14.
I-ECM inikezela ngendawo yokugcina esembindini nokufikelela
kulwazi kwakunye nokungqinelana nokulandelela wonke amasebe ephondo jikelele.
Ukuphunyezwa kwe-ECM kuza kuzisa iinguqu ezingummangaliso ekufezekisweni
kweenkqubo zoshishino neenkqubo ezijolise ekunyuseni ukusebenza, uxanduva
nokungafihlisi.
Ukutshintshwa kwe-ECM kuRhulumente weNtshona Koloni kuzokwenza i- DCAS, ibinjengomgcini wephondo wolawulo lwamaxwebhu. Ukunyanzelisa umgaqo-
Ukufakwa kwamaxwebhu ekhompyutheni ezinto ezigciniweyo ziza kukhawulelana
neemfuno zabo bancedwayo nokukhuthaza ukumiswa kolawulomela nokubonelela
ngokufikelela kwikhomyutha kumaxwebhu agciniweyo.
ekhomyutheni kubanjwe kwiZiko loLondolozo lweeNkcukacha eziBalulekileyo kuza
kuqhubeka kusebenzisa i-software ye-WCG-approved OpenText Content Server software.
Amaxwebhu okusebenza nawo aza kuskenwa.
Iteknoloji entsha itshintsha umsebenzi wabagcini bendawo, neenkqubo zoqeqesho
lwangaphakathi iza kuqhuba nokuphucula izakhono zabasebenzi.
Imigaqo-nkqubo, iindlela zokusebenza, nemigaqo iza kuphuhliswa ukuphucula iinkonzo
eziya kubathengi nokuphumeza imisebenzi ekumgangatho ophezulu yehlabathi yolawulo
lwamaxwebhu neerekhodi.  Ukubonelelwa ngamaxwebhu agciniweyo kubaphandi kwigumbi lokufundela kuza
Oku kuzogcina unxulumano
olubalulekileyo phakathi kwezinto zakudla nezelixesha.
Ubudlelane obumiyo neGenealogical Society of Utah nokufakwa kwamaxwebhu ekhompyutheni kuza kuqhuba.
Imisebenzi yokwazisa iza kuqhutywa kwiindawo zoluntu, ukufundisa uluntu ngokubanzi
nokudlala indima ebalulekileyo ekuxhaseni uluntu olunamathuba avulelekileyo.
Ulutsha liqela elingundoqo ekujoliswe kulo ukuxhasa i-WCG ukuba ifikelele kwiinjongo zayo
malunga nokubandakanywa koluntu.
Ukuthatha inxaxheba kwi-National Automated Archival Retrieval Information System (NAAIRS) kuza kuqhuba.
Abathathi-nxaxheba kwisicwangciso sokuphucula ukuhanjiswa kweenkozo kuza kuqhuba
ngokubhalisa bonke abaphandi kuluhlu olusekhompyutheni ukuququzelela unxibelelwano
nabo.  INkonzo yoLondolozo lweeNkcukacha eziBalulekileyo yeNtshona Koloni iza kuqhuba
eziBalulekileyo.
