Ingxaki yethu
Utywala bubangela owona monakalo mkhulu eluntwini lwethu kunokuba
sicinga, kwaye kushokoxeke inkxaso ekulungiseni umonakalo owenziwe
nasekukhutshweni kwelayisensi, kwimveliso, ekuhanjisweni nasekuthengisweni
kotywala, kodwa ayiyijongi impembelelo neziphumo zomonakalo onxulumene
ukogqitha abantu amaninzi bamanye amazwe, kwaye oko bakwenza
ngeendlela ezohlukeneyo ezingumngcipheko. Umlinganiselo wokuselwa
notywala.
Utywala sesona siyobisi sisetyenziswa gwenxa kweli lizwe liphela. Ngo-
2013, babonwa njengonobangela wesi-3 okhokelela kumngcipheko wokufa
nokukhubazeka eMzantsi Afrika, kulandele ukuzibandakanya kwezesondo
ngaphandle kokhuseleko nasekutyebeni.
Kwakhona kusesona siyobisi
siphala phambili ekusetyenzisweni gwenxa eNtshona Koloni.
