IMBULAMBETHE KASIHLALO
Unyaka-mali wama-2013/14 ubungunyaka wotshintsho kwiLifa leMveli leNtshona
Koloni (HWC) sibona ukuphela kwexesha leBhunga lalo kunye nokonyulwa
kweBhunga elitsha eliza kusebenza kude kube yeyeThupha yowama-2016.
Ngeli
xesha kukho abantu abaqhelekileyo abaninzi kwibhunga lesine, maninzi amalungu
amatsha athe, ngenxa yamagalelo awo enziwe kwangethuba, abe sele
ezibonakalise ukuba ongeze ixabiso eliqaphelekayo lokusebenza kwilifa lemveli leli phondo.
Laura Robinson
Sifundile ke ngamava, iKomiti ephumayo isebenze ngokuzinikela ngokuthi yamkele
umgaqo-nkqubo ofuna ukuqinisekisa uphazamiseko olunokuba khona wokuba
ixesha lotshintsho lweekomiti wawulawulwe luphazamiso oluncinci olwalukho
ekusebenzeleni uluntu. Ukuze sikuphumeze ke oku, eli Bhunga lingenayo ngoku liphinde lonyula
kwakhona iikomiti ebezikade zikhona phantsi koosihlalo abatsha kwixesha elifutshane lethutyana ukuze
kuvulelwe ixesha elaneleyo lokuba kukufunwa amalungu amatsha aze onyulwe.
Le nto iqinisekise
ukuba amalungu ekomiti, angawona mahashe aphala phambile asebenzayo eli qumrhu, akhethwa
emva kokuba iBhunga elitsha lineenyanga ezimbalwa ukuba lizinze noosihlalo abatsha sele
beqhelekile benomda kunye noxanduva lweekomiti zabo.
Ngeli xesha sele kusonjululwe ukuba
umgaqo-nkqubo ufanele uphinde ujongwe ngaphambi kokuba liphele ixesha leli Bhunga likhoyo,
kuvakala ngokubanzi ukuba le nkqubo ingcono kunale ibisetyenziswa eyayiyeyokuba iBhunga
elingenayo kufuneka lonyule iikomiti kwintlanganiso yalo yokuqala.
Eyona nto iqatshelweyo kumsebenzi we-HWC kunyaka ophelileyo ibikukwanda kwama-60% kwinani
lezicelo ezifunyenweyo kwaza kwasetyenzwa ngazo.
Oku kwanda kushishino lokwakha kubonakalise
umngeni kwiqumrhu othe wasokola ukunqongophala kwabasebenzi kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo.
Inani lamagosa elifa lemveli aziingcali lingaphantsi ngesiqingatha kunangaphambili.
Nangona kunjalo,
kungenxa yomsebenzi onzima wabasebenzi kunye namalungu ekomiti eyathi i-HWC yanakho
ukulawula oku kwanda komsebenzi kwaqatshelwayo.
Kukho ithemba lokuba, kunyaka-mali wama-2014/15, uRhulumente weNtshona Koloni, njengomqeshi
wabasebenzi be-HWC, uza kube eyisombulule imingeni ngokuphathelele kwingqesho.
Inkqubo
ekhoyo yengqesho idala inkxalabo yokusebenza ekufuneka iqwalaselwe kunye nefuthe elibi kulingano
lweenkonzo ezinikezelwa kuluntu.
Kwakhona idala ubunzima kwingqesho kwicandelo eliqatyelwe
zizakhono.
Inkqubo ecothayo yengqesho kwakhona ikhokelela ekubeni kuphulukwane nabantu
Ngeli xesha kukho oku kwanda kwezicelo, umsebenzi kunye nemeko yomngeni wabasebenzi, unyaka
ophelileyo ubungomnye apho iqumrhu belikwazi ukwenza umsebenzi omncinci kakhulu endaweni
yokuba kusetyenzwe ngezicelo.
Ukulawula olu xinzelelo luninzi bekungazukukwazi ukwenzeka ngaphandle kokuzinikela okumandla
kwicala lamalungu eBhunga langoku nelangaphambili, iikomiti zalo ezisisgxina, kunye nabasenzi
abazinikeleyo.
Mandithathe eli thuba ndibulele kubo bonke oogxa bethu, neSebe leMicimbi
yeNkcubeko neMidlalo (DCAS) elinike i-HWC inkxaso ngokuqhubekayo, nokuqapheleka kakhulu
kwicandelo lokulawula imali.
Ilizwi lombulelo liya kuMphathiswa owehlayo uGqr Ivan Meyer, othe ngeli
xesha lakhe lokusebenza wangumxhasi onemincili kumsebenzi wethu.
Egameni le-HWC,
ndimnqwenelela okuhle kwimisebenzi yakhe emitsha kwiKhabinethi yePhondo.
