Loo nyaka uphelileyo ibingomnye apho eli qumrhu belinenkcitho eninzi,
ngokuhambelana nokujoliswe kuko kokuhanjiswa kweenkonzo, kunikezelwe kakhulu
kwinkxaso yeBhunga neekomiti zalo.
Uninzi lomsebenzi owayanyaniswa noko
kukubuyiselwa imali kwicala elikhulu elayanyaniswa nokuba kusetyenzwe ngezicelo.
Kunyaka esijonge kuwo, ukusebenza ngezicelo ibingumba omkhulu womsebenzi
apho iLifa leMveli leNtshona Koloni belikwazi ukuba libe yinxenye.
Konke ebekujoliswe
kuko kwiSicwangciso soMsebenzi woNyaka kufikelelwe kuko okanye kwedlulwa.
Andrew Hall
Ngeli xesha kwakukho into eyayilindelekile ekuqaleni konyaka yokuba eminye
imisebenzi isenakho ukwenzeka, ngenxa yezizathu ezayanyaniswa nokwanda
kwinani lezicelo ezifunyenweyo kunye nokucotha kokuqeshwa kwabasebenzi
abatsha, le nto ingqine ukuba, inxenye eninzi, ingangenzeki.
Ukwanda kwezicelo kwixesha lokucwangcisa imali leminyaka emithathu, njengoko kuchaziwe,
kukhokelele ekujongweni kwakhona kwendlela zokusebenza kunye nokuphuculwa kokwanela kwezinto.
Nangona kunjalo, ukwanda kwezicelo kunyaka wama-2013/14 kukhokelele
ekuqwalaselweni kwendlela ubuchwephetshe ngokwendlela yenkqubo yolawulo lweenkcukacha
(IMS) obunganceda ngayo eli qumrhu kwicala lengxaki yolawulo.
Ekupheleni konyaka-mali,
isivumelwano sophuhliso saloo nkqubo saye sapapashwa kwaza kwachazwa eza kuliphuhlisa.
Njengenyathelo elijolise kwinxenye yokunceda kumsebenzi, inkqubo yokuvolontiya kwi-HWC
eyaqaliswa kunyaka ophelileyo, yamiselwa ngokungcono.
Ngaphandle kokuncediswa ngabafundi
nabo basanda kufumana izidanga abafuna amava omsebenzi kwicandelo lemithombo yelifa lemveli,
eli qumrhu ngelingakhange likuphumeze oko belijolise kuko kulo nyaka.
Ngowama-2013/14, i-HWC ivule i-akhawunti yotyalo-mali nemali ebekelwe iprojekthi ye-IMS bucala
kwaye ezinye iinjongo zityalelwe imali ngokokhukhuphiswano.
Imali yokuqala ebekujoliswe kuyo kule
yale njongo sele ixabangelwe yingeniso yentlawulo yezicelo apho i-HWC sele iqalisile ukuhlawula,
ngokuhambelana nomsebenzi wamanye amagunya emithombo yelifa lemveli.
Emva komhla wokwenza ingxelo, kwafakwa ibango le-R26 574 804 kwi-HWC, iDCAS kunye neSebe
ngomhla we-8 kwekaCanzibe yama-2014.
Eli bango lafakwa yi-Midnight Storm Investments 170 (Pty)
Ltd kwaye livela ekukhatyweni kwesicelo phantsi kwecandelo lama-27 le-NHRA elalifakwe kunyaka-
mali wama-2011/12 laza lakhatywa okokugqibela kwisibheno yiTribunal eyayifunwe nguMphathiswa
ngomhla wama-21 kweyeNkanga yowama-2013.
Ukuqukumbela, ndithatha eli thuba ndibulele amalungu eBhunga langaphambili le-HWC ngenkonzo
yabo kunye nokuzinikela kwixesha ebelimisiwe leminyaka emithathu ndiphinde ndamkele iBhunga
elitsha elisele likubonakalisile ukuzinikela ekubhekiseni phambili umsebenzi welo belikhona ngaphambili
ngomoya ofanayo.
Imibulelo emininzi iya kumsebenzi ngamnye, amavolontiya kunye namalungu
ekomiti asebenzele eli qumrhu ngokuzinikela okukhulu besebenza kumngeni wonyaka wovavanyo.
Inkxaso neengcebiso zogxa bam abakwiqela labalawuli abakhulu beSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko
neMidlalo ngayo yonke indlela yemiba ebhekiselele kwi-HWC, ndiyayibulela, kwaye ndiya kuhlala
ndiyibulela.
bequmrhu loluntu.
Kwakhona ndiyabulela kuMphathiswa wethu owehlayo, uGqr u-Ivan Meyer,
neNtloko yeSebe lakhe u-Adv Estienne Pretorius.
Inkxaso yabo nokundibonisa umkhomba-ndlela kulo
