6.1 UMBONO
Ukubhiyozela, ukuxabisa, ukugcina kakuhle nokukhulisa imithombo yelifa lemveli eyahlukeneyo
yasezidolophini nasemaphandleni yabantu baseNtshona Koloni ngokukhuthaza ukuzingca kwilifa
lemveli elibonakalayo nelingabonakaliyo, ngokukodwa kwindawo ebezikade zihlelelekile.
6.2 Umnqophiso
Ngokumisela, ukuphumeza nokugcina kakuhle isicwangciso-qhinga solawulo lwelifa lemveli
esimanyeneyo nesisebenzayo eNtshona Koloni, siza kuqinisekisa ukubonakaliswa, ukulondoloza kunye
nokukhuthazwa okucwangcisiweyo kwemithombo yelifa lemveli kulo lonke uluntu ukwenzela
isizukulwana sangoku nesexesha elizayo.
6.3
Iimpawu zentsulungeko Ukukhuthaza ukuzibandakanya kuluntu, ukuphucula ukuzingca ngokuba ungummi, intembeko,
ukukwazi ukuphendula nokukhathala.
UMTHETHO NEZINYE IZIGUNYAZISO
I-HWC yamiselwa ngomhla we-5 kweyeDwarha yowama-2010 njengegunya lemithombo yelifa lemveli
lephondo ngokoMthetho weMithombo yeLifa leMveli weSizwe, we-1999.
Iphantsi kweMithetho
kaNondyebo weSizwe kuye neShedyuli yesi-3 yequmrhu loluntu lwephondo ngokwe-PFMA.
I-HWC iyalelwe ukuba iphuhlise izicwangciso-qhinga kunye neenkqubo zokuba kuphunyezwe i-NHRA.
Ezi zinto zibandakanya ukuchongwa, ukushicilela, ukukhusela, ukulondoloza ukukhuthaza nokulawulwa
kwelifa lemveli kweli phondo.
