2 AMAGQABANTSHINTSHI NGOKUSEBENZA KWEQUMRHU
Isimo sonikezelo lweenkonzo
Uphawu olungundoqo lwesimo sonikezelo lweenkonzo ibikukunqongophala kwabasebenzi
Le nto yenze ukuba unyaka-mali wama-
2013/14 ube ngomnye onzima kakhulu kubalawuli babasebenzi kunye neekomiti zeLifa leMveli
leNtshona Koloni.
Abasebenzi abaziingcali abanoxanduva lomgodlo weenzame ezibandakanywa
ekuqhubeni izicelo behle ukusuka kwisibhozo ukuya kwisithathu kwaye oko kwakusenzeka phantsi
kweemeko zoxinzelelo olukhulu zokuba okujoliswe kuko komsebenzi kufikelelwe kuko kwaye ugunyaziso
lwequmrhu lokuqhuba nezicelo kumaxesha ewayebekiwe kufikelelwe kulo.
Le mpumelelo yajongwa
ngakwicala lokukhula kwenani lezicelo ezifunyenweyo ezingama-60%, kuphuculwe iimeko zoqoqosho
ekwakhiweni kwecandelo loqoqosho.
Ngokubhekiselele koku, iqumrhu lancedwa yi-archaeologist
eyaqeshwa ngesivumelwano esasiqala phakathi kweyeKhala kwaza kwikota yokugqibela kwangena
amavolontiya amabini, elinye lingumfundi wocwangciso lwedolophu owayengawufumani msebenzi
owayefuna amava obungcali kulondolozo lwelifa lemveli.
La mavolontiya asebenza iintsuku ezine
ngeveki.
Enye yezinto ezibangela ubunzima evela kwiimeko zabasebenzi iLifa leMveli leNtshona Koloni ilenze
laphantse alakwazi ukunikezela eyona ngcebiso ibifuneka kunye noncedo lwabenzi-zicelo
abangenakho ukumelana neenkonzo ezinobungcali zeengcali zelifa lemveli.
Ukungabikho komyili
wezakhiwo oyingcali kubasebenzi ukususela ekupheleni kweyeNkanga ibiyinkxababo ethile. Siyinikiwe
kuqeshwe abayili bezakhiwo.
Le nto iye yacaca xa umsebenzi okwinqanaba lokuqala lemivuzo eye
wachongelwa ukuvala isithuba somsebenzi seGosa leLifa leMveli loKwakha okuSingqongileyo
kwicandelo elikhulu ngenxa yomvuzo ebeliza kuwuhlawulwa.
