Ukuqwalaselwa koluhlu lweempahla nomhlaba wesizwe
Apha ekuhambeni konyaka kwagqitywa ukuhlolwa koluhlu lwempahla zoMasipala waseDrakenstein
zemithombo yelifa lemveli.
Uluhlu lweempahla olutsha lomhlaba wesizwe lwafunyanwa kwiindawo ezimbini ezikuMasipala
waseStellenbosch, enye ingokubaluleka kwembali yeseStellenbosch ize enye iyeyeYunivesithi
yaseStellenbosch.
Kwafunyanwa nolunye uluhlu lwempahla oluseChurch Street, iTulbagh kuMasipala
waseWitzenberg.
Ekupheleni konyaka ezi zintlu kunye noluhlu loMasipala waseGeorge olwangeniswa
kunyaka-mali ongaphambili bezisaqwalaselwa.
Uluhlu lweempahla oluseChurch Street, iTulbagh lolwesibini olungeniswe liqumrhu lolondolozo
elibhalisileyo, kwaye lubonakalisa into eyiyo apho abantu bathatha uxanduva lokuchonga imithombo
yelifa lemveli ebalulekileyo.
Inkqubo yokuhlola uluhlu lweempahla zeSixeko saseKapa iyaqhubeka kwaye kulindeleke ukuba kuza
kugqitywa kunyaka wama-2016.
Izinto eziza kulungiswa kuluhlu lweempahla loMasipala iSwartland, olungeniswe ngowama-2011,
zisalindile.
Ukungeniswa kwezintlu zeempahla kubalulekile ngenxa yezizathu ezininzi.
Kwenza isiseko sokubona
ukhuseleko olusemthethweni lweendawo zeCandelo loku-1 lweSahluko se-II se-NHRA nasekuboneni
umgangatho weendawo ezinceda iHWC kunye norhulumente wamakhaya ukuba aqonde iimpawu
Ngokubhekiselele kule yamva, ukungeniswa
koluhlu lweempahla kulincede kakhulu eli qumrhu ngokujonga umifanekiso eqingqiweyo yesizwe
yakudala kunye nendlela ephawulwe ngayo kamva neembasa ezibonakalisa ubume bazo njengeendawo zelifa lemveli lephondo.
Le nto nje ngokukodwa iyinyaniso kuMasipala waseDrakenstein
apho yonke imifanekiso eqingqiweyo yesizwe yangaphambili ilungiswe ngokomgangatho.
Ngaphezu kwento yonke, injongo yoluhlu lweempahla ibonakalisa ubukho bemithombo yelifa lemveli
kwiindawo ezibonakalayo kwaye le nto inegalelo elikhulu kumandla abo baphuhlisa ucwangciso
ukuphepha ingxabano kunye nabasemagunyeni bemithombo yelifa lemveli nokusebenzisa imithombo
Ke ngoku zinexabiso elikhulu
kakhulu njengento yokusombulula inkxalabo phakathi kolondolozo lwelifa lemveli kwelinye icala kunye
nemfuno yokuphuhlisa kwelinye icala.
Izintlu zempahla kwakhona zilinyathelo lokuqala elibalulekileyo ekuchongeni iindawo zokukhusela
indawo zelifa lemveli ngokweCandelo lama-31 le-NHRA kunye nezicwangciso zokwahlula umhlaba.
Uninzi lwezo ndawo lwachongwa kwizintlu ezisele zivunyiwe kwaye le yindawo efuna ukulandelelwa
ngoomasipala abachaphazelekayo.
2.2.4
Ukubhengezwa kweendawo zelifa lemveli zephondo kunye nokunikezelwa kweembasa
Ngomhla wama-29 kweyeNkanga yowama-2013, iSaron Mission Station kwilali yaseSaron
yabhengezwa njengendawo yelifa lemveli yephondo ngokuthi kuqwalaselwe imbonakalo yayo
akhululekileyo, kunye nobuncutshe ekuyileni izakhiwo.
Imbasa ebonakalisa ubume bendawo yatyhilwa
15 nguGqr Ivan Meyer ngexesha lenkonzo yesikhumbuzo kwinkonzo imission ngeCawa umhla woku-1
kweyoMnga yowama-2013, umhla osisikhumbuzo zonyaka we-175 sokukhululeka kwamakhoboka
kwiKoloni yangaphambili.
Kulo nyaka sijolise kuwo, iHWC ikhuphe iimbasa ezingama-63 eziphawula iindawo zelifa lemveli
zephondo.
Ezi zinto zibandakanya leyo intsha ebhengezwe njengeSaron Mission, kunye nomfanekiso
oqingqiweyo wesizwe wangaphambili othe walungiswa wasemgangathweni.
lwakuMasipala waseDrakenstein lusuka ekungenisweni koluhlu loomasipala, kunye neClanwilliam, apho
Eminye imisebenzi ebandakanya urhulumene wamakhaya
Ngexesha lonyaka wama-2013/14, kwakukho ingxoxo iyayiqhubeka kunye neCoCT malunga nomba
wokunikezelwa kwamagunya.
Lo mba wawujikeleze impikiswano eyayikhona kumanyathelo
abhekiselele kwiinkqubo zezibongozo ezenziwe kwiNHRA kunye noRhulumente waMakhaya:uMthetho
weeNkqubo zikaMasipala, wama-2000. KweyoKwindla yowama-2014 loo mba wabonakala ngathi
2.2.6
Inyanga yeLifa leMveli  iprojekthi iWiki Loves Monuments
Kwakhona iHWC ibonelele imisebenzi yeNtshona Koloni yeprojekthi iWiki Loves Monuments.
Eli nyathelo
leWikipedia kungokunje lineminyaka emine likhona kwaye lilelesibini xa kubandakanywa uMzantsi
Afrika.
Ngokusebenzisa umnatha-zwe
kunye nobuchwephetshe beselula, olu khuphiswano lunomtsalane kulutsha kwaye luyalubandakanya
kwiprojekthi ukuze lushicilele iindawo zelifa lemveli.
Oku kwenza ushicilelo lwemithombo yelifa lemveli
exabiseke kakhulu kwabasemagunyeni belifa lemveli.
Imifanekiso engama-6 432 iyonke zaseMzantsi
Afrika yaye yakhutshwa ngexesha lenyanga yoMsintsi yowama-2013 kwaye iHWC kungokunje ingene
kwisivumelwano sobonelelo lweminyaka emithathu kwiWikiMedia yaseMzantsi Afrika.
Owona mfanekiso uxhonywe phezulu kakhulu eNtshona Koloni, othe waphuma kwindawo yesithathu
Wawuthathwe ngumsebenzi wangaphambili
weHWC ekungokunje ajike wayingcali ekuthatheni imifanekiso, uChris Snelling owaphuma kwindawo
yesithathu kukhuphiswano lowama-2012.
2.2.7
Ukufaka iinkcukacha ekhompyutheni ukuze zifundeke
Iprojekthi ebonelelwa ngemali yeNkqubo yeMisebenzi yoLuntu eyaNdisiweyo (EPWP) eqhubekayo
benze inkqubela engenaziphazamiso kuzo zonke iziphazamiso ezingenayo ezazingafunyanwa
ngohlobo lobuchwephetshe olwathi lwaskenwa lwaze lwagcinwa.
Le projekthi iqeshe abantu abatsha
abane.
Ukongeza koku, ngama-7 472 oshicilelo olungama-15 576 lulonke olukwindawo yoGcino-
maxwebhu olusele luskeniwe. Emva kokuba kwenziwe ingqwalasela kunye nengxoxo neSAHRA, iHWC igqibe ekubeni ingathathi
nxaxheba kwiprojekthi yeSAHRIS (iNkqubo yeeNkcukacha zeMithombo yeLifa leMveli loMzantsi
Afrika).
Isigqibo sathathwa ngokusekelwe kwizinto ezininzi, enye yazo kuyimfuno yokudibana nezinye
iinkqubo kwinqanaba lephondo nelikamasipala, ngokukodwa neNkonzo zoLondolozo lweMbali
zephondo kunye neNkqubo yeeNkcukacha zeSithuba esiManyeneyo (ISIS) seCoCT kunye nezinto
ezilulutho zokuba yinxenye yeprojekthi yolawulo lomxholo woshishino loRhulumente weNtshona Koloni
ekhokhelwe kwiDCAS nalapho iHWC iza kwenza inzuzo eza kuthi iqatshelwe.
Kwakhona kwakukho
nenkxalabo yokuba xa inikezelwe loo mthwalo womsebenzi umninzi iHWC iqhubeka nezicelo, kwaye
amanani amakhulu ezicelo ezifunyenweyo, ixesha eliye liphela kunye neminye imiba yokuhanjiswa
kweenkonzo enento yokwenza ngaphezulu kwiSAHRIS apho iHWC ingenakuba nalawulo
ingachaphazela kakhulu uhanjiso lweenkonzo ngokunempumelelo.
Ekupheleni konyaka-mali , iHWC ingene kwisivumelwano neDCAS ukuba kuphuhliswe inkqubo yolawulo
lweenkcukacha (IMS) ukuze iyisebenzise kunye neeNkonzo zoLondolozo lweMbali ize ibize ixabiso
ngokwesivumelwano esikhoyo seSITA ebesipapashiwe.
Inkqubo eza kuqala ukuphuhlisa kunyaka-mali
okwangoku isaziwa ngokuba yi HIMS  iNkqubo yoLawulo lweeNkcukacha zeLifa leMveli.
Ibonwa
njengeprojekthi eza kuvumela ukuba kwenziwe izicelo ngokobuchwephetshe phantsi kweNHRA kwaye iza kukhawulezisa imisebenzi eminzi ekungoku nje isenziwa ngezandla.
Le misebenzi yongezwa
kwimisebenzi yokuqhuba nomsebenzi weenkcukacha kunye nokugcinwa nokufikelela kumaxwebhu.
Kulindeleke ukuba le nkqubo yenze ifayili ezingama-15 500 zeHWC zifikeleleke ngokukhawuleza
eluntwini kwaye iza kwenza abasebenzi abaziingcali bakhululeke baqwalasele kakhulu ngokukodwa
kwimisebenzi abayiqeshelweyo.
Imigaqo-nkqubo esunguliweyo neenguqu kwimithetho
2.3.1
Ukuphuhliswa komgaqo-nkqubo
Umgaqo-nkqubo ongokonyula iikomiti waphuhliswa kwangethuba kulo nyaka-mali waza wanceda
kakhulu kwixesha lokutshintsha emva kokuba iBhunga leLifa leMveli leNtshona Koloni liqalise
Ngokuchasene nexesha elidlulileyo apho
kwiintlanganiso zalo zokuqala iBhunga elitsha kwakufuneka lonyule iikomiti ukuze likwazi ukwenza
umsebenzi wequmrhu uqhubeke ungaphazanyiswanga, lo mgaqo-nkqubo uvumela iikomiti ezikhoyo
ukuba ziqhubeke zisebenza kwixesha lotshintsho ngexesha apho izicelo kufuneka zisebenze ezikomitini
luze ulonyulo lwenziwe xa iBhunga sele liyazi imisebenzi yalo.
Xa kulandelwa inyathelo elithathwe ekuqaleni kwexesha lokusebenza leBhunga langaphambili, lonke
ulawulo, imithetho, imigaqo-nkqubo, izikhokelo kunye neencwadi ezisebenza ngondoqo wogunyaziso
lwequmrhu zenziwa zayincwadi ephathekayo, incwadi ebhaliweyo eyayinikwe ilungu ngalinye
leBhunga elitsha kunye nabasebenzi kweyoMsintsi.
Ekwikhompyutha sele isasazwe ngokubanzi kwaye
isoloko ihlaziywa xa kusenziwa utshintsho.
2.3.2
Imiba yasemthethweni
Ngeli xesha kungekho zihlomelo kulawulo okanye imithetho, kwafunwa iimbono zasemthethweni
ezininzi ezazibhekiselele kwinkcazo yeNHRA kwaye ezi zinto zanceda ukucacisa iindlela eziya kwindawo
ekungaqinisekwanga ngazo ngakwicala leHWC nabo bangenisa izicelo kwiqumrhu.
Zininzi kwakhona
iziganeko apho iHWC isebenzisa amagunya ayo ukuphelisa oko kubizwa njengokuba ngumsebenzi ongekho mthethweni kwaye ityala lasenkundleni liyaqhubeka.
Imiba engundoqo ixoxwa
ngokucacileyo kakuhle apha ngezantsi.
