IGosa elinoXanduva (AA) leLifa l;eMveli yeNtshona Koloni (HWC), lenza umsebenzi wokuphumeza
uLawulo loMgcipheko kuShishino (ERM) ngokuhambelana neNkqubo-sikhokelo yoLawulo loMgcipheko
kwiCandelo loLuntu kuNondyebo weSizwe (NTPSRMF) kwaye iCandelo loLawulo loMngcipheko
woShishino (D:ERM) elikwiQumrhu leNkulumbuso linikezela ngenkonzo yenkxaso enobuchule ebumbeneyo kwiQumrhu.
(NTPSRMF) nokungenisa ngakumbi ulawulo lomngcipheko kwiqumrhu loluntu, uRhulumente weNtshona
Koloni (WCG) usebenzise uMgaqo-nkqubo we-ERM oveza injongo iyonke ye-WCG ngokubhekiselele kwi- ERM.
Isicwangciso-qhinga soNyaka sokuPhumeza i-ERM senzelwe ukuba senze umgaqo-nkqubo we-WCG
ERM usebenze kwaye uphumeze isiCwangciso soNyaka sokuPhumeza uLawulo loMngcipheko
weShishini kunye nezinto eziphambili zolawulo lomngcipheko kwiQumrhu.
Le nto yenza ukuba eli
qumrhu likwazi ukuphumeza iinjongo zalo kunye nezalathisi zomsebenzi, ukuphucula ukuthathwa
kwezigqibo ezichaziweyo zomngcipheko kuze kuthotyelwe ngokukuko ulawulo olusebenzayo.
Kwakhona sibonakalisa iindima kunye noxanduva lwabalawuli kunye nabasebenzi ekungeniseni
ulawulo lomngcipheko kweli qumrhu size sivumele ulawulo, imimiselo, iindlela, izixhobo kunye
nemithombo ukuba isetyenziselwe ukuqinisekisa isicwangciso se-ERM.
IKomiti yoLawulo loMgcipheko noBuqhetseba inikezela ngolongamelo lolawulo kuyo yonke inkqubo
yolawulo lomngcipheko lwequmrhu ize ibonelele ngeengxelo eziphathelele kumsebenzi wolawulo
lomgcipheko kwiGosa elinoXanduva.
IKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi inikezela ngolongamelo oluzimeleyo
lwenkqubo yequmrhu yolawulo lomngcipheko.
IKomiti yoPhicothozincwadi yanikezela iingxelo zekota
zenkqubela ze-ERM kunye nembonakalo yomngcipheko wequmrhu kunye neerejista ukuze lenze
indima yalo ezimeleyo yokongamela. Uhlolo lweKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi lwenkqubo yolawulo
lomngcipheko linxulumene nenkqubo nenkqubela yokuphunyezwa kwesiCwangciso soNyaka
sokuPhunyezwa i-ERM yequmrhu kunye nemingcipheko ebonakalayo/enobuchule elijamelene nayo
iqumrhu, kunye neempendulo ezifanelekileyo zomngcipheko/ izicwangciso-qhinga zokuwunqanda.
IKomiti yoLawulo lobuQhophololo noMngcipheko (FARMACO)
Eli qumrhu limisele iFARMCO ukuba incede iGosa elinoXanduva ekwenzeni imisebenzi yakhe yolawulo
lomngcipheko.
Le komiti isebenza ngaphantsi kwemiqathango emiselwe liGosa elinoXanduva.
Le
komiti kufuneka ihlangane kane ngonyaka.
