INkqubo yoLawulo loMngcipheko
Kweli xesha kujongwe kulo, eli Qumrhu livavanya imingcipheko elinokuthi libe nayo kwisicwangciso salo
esinobuchule kunye nesomsebenzi wonyaka.
Uhlolo lomngcipheko lwenziwa ngokomgangatho
onobuchule rhoqo ngonyaka luze luhlaziywe rhoqo ngekota. Ngokomgangatho wenkqubo, uhlolo
lomngcipheko lwenziwa rhoqo ngekota ukuze kujongwe kuze kuhlaziywe imingcipheko ekhoyo kwaye
kubonwe nemingcipheko eqalayo.
ngokokuthanda kwabo nangokwefuthe; izicwangciso zokunqanda umngcipheko ziyenziwa zize
zilawulwe ngabanini bomngcipheko ababelweyo.
Ababhalisi benkqubo yomngcipheko bamkelwa
ngumlawuli ofanelekileyo wenkqubo.
IFARMCO ilungisa, ibeke phambili ize indulule ngakumbi kwiGosa elinoXanduva ukuba yeyiphi
imingcipheko obonakalayo osele uthomalalisiwe onempendulo yomngcipheko efanelekileyo/
ukunqandwa ukuze ukhawulelane neenjongo ezinobuchule zeQumrhu. Le nkqubo yenziwa rhoqo
ngekota kwaye inceda ixhase kuhlolo lwemeko yomsebenzi weQumrhu.
ICANDELO LOLAWULO LWANGAPHAKATHI
Kungumsebenzi weGosa elinoXanduva ukuhlola ngokuqhubekayo nokuvavanya ulawulo
lwangaphakathi ukuqinisekisa ukuba imisebenzi yolawulo ekhoyo iyasebenza, iyanelisa kwaye icacile
ize ihlaziywe xa kukho imfuneko.
Ukuphumeza oku, bekuhlalwa iintlanganiso ezingundoqo zolawulo
rhoqo ngekota kunye noMphicothi-zincwadi Jikelele, abaphathi benkqubo beSebe leMicimbi
yeNkcubeko neMidlalo kunye noMEC.
uphicotho-zincwadi olungenachaphaza kweli Qumrhu.
UPHICOTHO LWANGAPHAKATHI NEEKOMITI ZOPHICOTHO-ZINCWADI
Uphicotho-zincwadi lwangaphakathi lunika abalawuli iinkonzo zokuzimela, ukuqinisekisa injongo kunye
nokuqhagamshelana ukongeza ixabiso nokuqhubeka kuphuculwa umsebenzi weQumrhu.
Lufanele
luwuncede iQumrhu ukuba liphumelele ukwenza iinjongo zalo ngokuzisa indlela enezicwangciso,
nehloniphekileyo yokuvavanya nokuphucula ulawulo olusebenzayo loLawulo, noLawulo lomngcipheko
neenkqubo zoLawulo.
Le misebenzi ingundoqo yenziwa ngale ndlela:
kuphunyezwe iinjongo zeQumrhu;
Ukuvavanya ukufaneleka nokusebenza ngokukuko kunye nokwenza igalelo lokuphucula
inkqubo yolawulo lomngcipheko;
Ukuncedisa iGosa elinoXanduva ukuba ligcine kakuhle ulawulo olwanelisayo nolusebenza
kakuhle ngokuvavanya olo ulawulo ukuze kujongwe ukusebenza kwalo kakuhle nokwanelisa
kwalo, kunye nokwenza izindululo zokuphucula.
IKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi imiselwe njengekomiti eyongamelayo, enikezela ngolongamelo
oluzimeleyo kulawulo, ulawulo lomngcipheko neenkqubo zolawulo kwiQumrhu, nto leyo ibandakanya
ulongamelo nemisebenzi ebhekiselele kwezi zinto:
Umsebenzi woPhicotho-zincwadi lwangaPhakathi;
Umsebenzi woPhicotho-zincwadi wangaPhandle (umPhicothi-zincwadi Jikelele woMzantsi Afrika );
Uxanduva lwequmrhu nokwenza ingxelo;
Imigaqo-nkqubo yoxanduva lwequmrhu;
Ukujongwa kolawulo koPhicotho-zincwadi woMzantsi Afrikakunye nengxelo yophicotho-
zincwadi; Ukujongwa kohlolo lonyaka lwequmrhu;
Ulawulo lomgcipheko wequmrhu;
Ulawulo lwangaPhakathi;
Iinjongo ezimisiweyo; kunye
Nendlela zokuziphatha nophando olunzulu.
