Akanaso 8 UTHOTYELO-MITHETHO NEMIGAQO
Iinkqubo nemigaqo-nkqubo ikhona ukuqinisekisa uthotyelo-mithetho nemigaqo.
URhulumente weNtshona Koloni usamkele isiCwangciso-qhinga esiLwa noRhwaphilizo esingqina
ukunganyamezeli kwaphela kweli Phondo ukumelana norhwaphilizo nobuqhophololo.
IQumrhu lisamkele isiCwangciso sokuNqanda ubuQhophololo kunye nesicwangciso sokuPhumeza ukuNqanda
ubuQhophololo esenza ukuba sisebenze isiCwangciso sokuNqanda ubuQhophololo.
Iindlela ezininzi zokuchaza izityholo zorhwaphilizo nobuqhopholo zimiselwe zikhona kwaye zichaziwe
ngokucacileyo kwisiCwangciso-qhinga sokuLwa ubuQhophololo sePhondo kunye nesiCwangciso
sokuNqanda ubuQhophololo seQumrhu.
oluNzulu sishicilelwa kwiNkqubo yoLawulo lwamaTyala sisetyenziswe njengesixhobo solawulo
sokuchaza inkqubela eyenziwe ngamatyala aphathelele kwiQumrhu nasekelezele kubalo-bantu
lePhondo neQumrhu .
Siyabakhusela abasebenzi abahlaba ikhwelo ngezinto ezikrokrelekayo
zobuqhophololo, urhwaphilizo nobusela ukuba ukuziveza kokukhuselekileyo (okkkt, hayi ngolunya).
Ithuba lokuhlala ungaziwa kuyamelwana nalo kuye namphi na umntu ufuna ukuchaza izenzo
zobuqhophololo, ubusela norhwaphilizo kwaye xa benze njalo buqu, ububona bugcinwa bukhuselekile
nguloo mntu bachaze kuye.
Xa ubusela norhwaphilizo bungqiniwe emva kokuba kugqitywe uphando, umsebenzi othathe
inkxaxheba kwezo zenzo uza kusiwa kwiingxoxo zoluleko.
Kuzo zonke ezo meko, ummeli we-WCG oza
kwenza iingxoxo zoluleko kufuneka ibe nguye owenza isindululo sokuba kugxothwe loo msebenzi
uchaphazelekayo.
Apho kufunyaniswe ukuba ubungqina besenzo solwaphulo-mthetho buyinyaniso
kwasekuqaleni, umba wolwaphulo-mthetho ichazwa kwiiNkonzo zaMapolisa oMzantsi Afrika.
Kulo nyaka-mali, kugqitywe uphando olu-1 olwenziwe liCandelo loPhando luqinisekisa ubuQhophololo
noRhwaphilizo.
Ekupheleni konyaka-mali kwashiyeke imiba emibi-2 kuluhlu lwamatyala eQumrhu.
