UNondyebo wePhondo uyalinceda eli sebe ukwenzela ukucutha umngcipheko wokukhetha icala xa
abanini okanye abalawuli beenkampani bekwangabasebenzi bakarhulumente apha eNtshona Koloni.
Le nto yenziwa ngokuthi kunikezelwe iinkcukacha ezisuka kuPERSAL (iNkqubo yeMivuzo yaBasebenzi)
malunga nabasebenzi bakarhulumente ababhaliswe njengabanini okanye abalawuli beenkampani.
Eli qumrhu liqinisekisa ukuba abo bantu bafumana ileta evunyiweyo yoMvuzo woMsebenzi
ongaPhandle koweeNkonzo zikaRhulumente ngaphambi kokuqhuba ushishino nabo.
Eli qumrhu alifumanisanga zenzo zomkhethe kulo naluphi na ushishino oluqukumbelwe ngabaxhasi.
Ukuba oko bekufunyanisiwe, loo mba ubuza kubonwa njengomsebenzi wobuqhopholo luLawulo
lweNkxaso yoShishino kuze, emva koko kwenziwe uphando olumandla, loo mxhasi uza kubonwa
njengomniki-nkonzo ongenakukhethwa.
