INGENISO Ingeniso ilinganiselelwa ngexabiso elifanelekileyo elinokuqatshelwa elifunyenweyo okanye ingeniso.
Ingeniso
ivunyelwa xa kunokwenzeka ukuba iinzuzo zoqoqosho oluzayo okanye inkonzo enokwenzeka iza kubakho
kwiqumrhu naxa isixa-mali sengeniso sinokwazi ukulinganiselwa, kwaye kufikelelwe kwindlela ethile yemisebenzi
yequmrhu.
Ingeniso evela ekuhanjisweni kweenkonzo ibonwa kwintsalela ngokomlinganiselo xa kugqitywa
uthengiselwano ngosuku lokwenza ingxelo.
Esi sixa-mali asibonwa njengesilinganiselwe ngokunyanisekileyo zide kuthengiselwano zisonjululwe.
