IMBULAMBETHE YENZIWA NGUSIHLALO
Kwisigaba sesibini seminyaka engamashumi amabini lithuba lokubonakalisa
ukuzibophelela kwethu kumalungelo olwimi.
Kwiziphiwo ezininzi esizifumene
ngomzabalazo wethu nangoMgaqo-siseko omtsha, esona sibalulekileyo sisiqinisekiso
samalungelo olwimi.
Eyona nto isondele emntwini ngaphandle kobuhle bakhe
lulwimi lwakhe lwemveli.
Ngokwenza isidima nokuba umntu azazi ukuba ungubani,
iintetho nomculo owenziwa ngolwimi lwakho lwemveli yeyona nto iphambili
emntwini.
Umnqophiso weKomiti yeeLwimi eNtshona Koloni kunyaka ophelileyo,
kunye nemisebenzi yokukhuthaza iinkqubo zolwimi, ukufunda nokusebenzisa uLwimi
lokuThetha ngezandla ekuhlaleni, bubungqina bokuzinikela kwethu ukuqinisekisa
ukulingana kweelwimi ezintathu ezisemthethweni zephondo  isiBhulu, isiNgesi
nesiXhosa.
Kusinike ithemba xa ilungu elimele uluntu oluThetha ngezandla, uNks
Mirriam Ganiso, liye layinxalenye yekomiti kulo nyaka kwenziwa ngawo uhlolo.
UNjing.
Rajendra Chetty
Amalungelo oluntu olwimi ajolise ekukhuthazeni ubulungisa kwezolwimi nokususwa okanye
ukuthintelwa kokungalingani kwiilwimi okunokwenzeka ngenxa yolwimi.
Okuzuzwayo ekuphunyezweni
kwala malungelo kuquka ilungelo lomntu ngamnye nelomntu wonke lokuzazi ukuba ungubani.
Ilungelo
lolwimi likwaquka ilungelo lokufunda ezinye iilwimi kuquka iilwimi ezisemthethweni ezisetyenziswa
kwiindawo ezinokuthatha inxaxheba kwiinkqubo zentlalo, zopolitiko nezoqoqosho.
Ubume benkqubela
yesakhelo somthetho nesomgaqo-nkqubo senze indawo yokuba kusetyenziswe amalungelo oluntu
olwimi.
Noxa kunjalo, izibonelelo kufuneka zibonelelwe ukuqinisekisa ukuba kuphunyezwa umgaqo-
nkqubo. Umgaqo-nkqubo weMfundo ngoLwimi (ka-1997) ujolise ekwenzeni izikolo zenze imigaqo-nkqubo
yolwimi ezikolweni ehambelana nemithetho-siseko yamalungelo olwimi nokugcina iilwimi zabo
ezithethwa emakhaya ngeli xesha bekwazi ukufumana ezinye iilwimi nokukhuthaza ukuthethwa
kweelwimi ezininzi.
Ukuphumeza ngendlela esebenzayo kwalo mgaqo-nkqubo kuyaqhubeka ukuba
nemingeni kwaye kuzishiya ngaphandle iilwimi ebezifudula zingasiwa so xa kujongwa kulwimi
olukhethwayo ekufundwa nekufundiswa ngalo.
Ngeli xesha ikho imigaqo-nkqubo, uluntu kufuneka
luhlale luvundlile ukuqinisekisa ukuba imigaqo-nkqubo iyaphunyezwa nokuthetha iilwimi ezininzi
kuyakhuthazwa.
Kuluvuyo ukwazi ukuba iSebe leMfundo esisiseko lifaka ulwimi lwesiNtu njengesinye
isifundo solwimi olongezelelweyo kuzo zonke izikolo zaseMzantsi Afrika.
Ngowama-2014, isampuli
yezikolo ezili-10 kwiphondo ngalinye ziza kuba nolwimi lwesiNtu, ngethemba lo mbono uza kukhuthaza
uxhase okulindelekileyo kweziphumo ezigqwesayo ekufundeni kwinkqubo yezikolo zikarhulumente.
IKomiti yeeLwimi eNtshona Koloni iqaphela ngombulelo umsebenzi omhle owenziwe kunyaka
ophelileyo licandelo leeNkonzo zoLwimi kwiSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko nezeMidlalo.
Icandelo
leeNkonzo zoLwimi lizama ukuphumeza uMgaqo-nkqubo woLwimi weNtshona Koloni ngokwemisebenzi
yeCandelo lokuGuqula, lokuHlela nelokuTolika neCandelo lokuPhumeza uMgaqo-nkqubo woLwimi. Eli
candela lizama ukuqinisekisa ukuba abahlali baseNtshona Koloni bayakwazi ukufikelela kwiinkonzo
besebenzisa ulwimi olusemthethweni abalukhethayo.
Ikwakhuthaza iilwimi ebezifudula zingasiwa so
noLwimi lokuThetha ngezandla lwaseMzantsi Afrika ngokweenkqubo zokwazisa uluntu nemisebenzi
ukukhuthaza ukuphuhla kwabo. IKomiti iqaphela ngombulelo inkxaso kunyaka ophelileyo yoMphathiswa weMicimbi yeNkcubeko
neMidlalo uGqr Ivan Meyer.
IKomiti yeeLwimi ikwazile ukufikelela kwiinjongo zayo nokuphumeza
ngempumelelo iinkqubo zayo noko ijolise kuko ngenxa yokuzinikela nokusebenzisana kwamalungu
eKomiti.
Ndiyababulela ngokungazenzisiyo oogxa bam kwiKomiti ngendima abayidlalileyo kunyaka
ophelileyo ngokuzibophelela ekubandakanyeni uluntu namalungelo oluntu kumntu wonke wephondo.
Ukuba nolunye ulwimi kukufumana umoya wesibini.
