IIKOMITI ZOPHICOTHO-ZINCWADI NOPHICOTHO-ZINCWADI LWANGAPHAKATHI
Uphicotho-zincwadi lwangaphakathi lubonelela ngolawulo lweenkonzo ezizimeleyo, zesiqinisekiso
esineenjongo nezokunika iingcebiso esenzelwe ukongeza ixabiso nokuphucula imisebenzi yeQumrhu.
Kufuneka lincedise iQumrhu ukufezekisa iinjongo ngokuza neendlela eziqhuba kakuhle nezilungileyo
ukuvavanya nokuphucula impumelelo yoLaawulo, uLawulo lokuseMngciphekweni neenkqubo
zoLawulo.
Le misebenzi ilandelayo iphambili yenziwa malunga noku:
Ukuhlola nokwenza izindululo ezifanelekileyo zokuphucula inkqubo yolawulo ukuphumeza
iinjongo zeQumrhu;
Ukuvavanya ukwanelisa nempumelelo kunye nokuba negalelo ekuphuculeni inkqubo yolawulo lokusemngciphekweni;
Ukuncedisa iGosa eliNika iNgxelo ekugcineniulawulo olunempumelelo nolusebenzayo
nokwenza izindululo zokuqhubela phambili nokuphucula okusisting.
Ikomiti yophicotho-zincwadi isekwe njengebhodi eyongameleyo, kubonelelwa ngokongamela
okuzimeleyo nolawulo, ulawulo lomngcipho neenkqubo zolawulo kwiQumrhu, okuquka ukongamela
noxanduva olunxulumene noku:
Umsebenzi woPhicotho-zincwadi ngaphandle (njengoko wenziwe noMphicothi-zincwadi
Jikelele waseMzantsi Afrika);
Umgaqo-nkqubo wocwangciso-mali wequmrhu;
Ukuhlola nokuphengulula ulawulo loMphicothi-zincwadi Jikelele woMzantsi Afrika nengxelo
Ukuphengulula ubeko-liso lwasenyakeni lwequmrhu;
Ulawulo lokusemngciphekweni kwiqumrhu;
Ulawulo lwangaphakathi;
Iinjongo ezicwangciswe kwangaphambili;
Iindlela zokuziphatha nophando lwasenkundleni.
