Ukuphumelela koLawulo lwangaPhakathi
Iqumrhu lincedwa liSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo kwaye akukho kusilela kulawulo
lwangaphakathi okuye kwachazwa kwinqanaba leQumrhu.
Ulawulo lonyaka neengxelo zenyanga/zekota
IQumrhu linike ingxelo ngenyanga nangekota kuNondyebo wePhondo ngokweemfuno ze-PFMA.
IKomiti yoPhicotho yanelisekile sisiqulatho nobulunga beengxelo zokusebenza nezimali ngekota
ezilungiselelwe liGosa eliNika iNgxelo yeQumrhu kunyaka ophantsi kohlolo.
Ukuvavanywa kweeNgxelo zeMali zoNyaka
Ikomiti yophicotho-zincwadi:
ihlole yaze yaxoxa ngeeNgxelo zeMali zoNyaka eziphicothiweyo njengoko zichazwe kwingxelo
yonyaka noMphicothi-zincwadi Jikelele woMzantsi Afrika kunye neGisa eliNika iNgxelo;
ihlole ingxelo yolawu zoMphicothi-zincwadi Jikelele woMzantsi Afrika neempendulo zabaphathi
ihlole iinkqubo zeQumrhu ukuqinisekisa uthotyelo nalapho kufaneleke khona oku kuchaziwe
kwiingxelo zonyaka zezimali;
ihlole iinkqubo zeQumrhu ukuqinisekisa ukuthobelana nomthetho nezibonelelo zolawulo;
ihlole inkcukacha kwiinjongo ezimiswe ngenxengaphambili njengoko kuchazwe kwingxelo
yonyaka; ihlole uhlenga-hlengiso lwezinto ezivela kuphicotho lweQumrhu
ihlole yaze yathi aphi kufaneleke khona yacebisa iinguqu kwiingxelo zezimali eziphakathi
njengoko zichazwe iQumrhu zeenyana ezintandathu eziphela ngowama-30 kweyoMsintsi 2013
