INTSHAYELELO KASIHLALO
Njengoko kwakunikwe ingxelo kunyaka ophelileyo, iKomishini yeNkcubeko
yeNtshona Koloni (WCCC) iwamkele umbono welungu leKomiti eLawulayo
yePhondo (MEC) yeMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo, uGq. Ivan Meyer
wokukhuthazwa kolwamkelo lwenkcubeko phakathi koluntu lwenkcubeko
Mr Mervyn Smith
IKomishini ixhasiwe ngobuchule nangokulungileyo ngabasebenzi beSebe
leMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo (DCAS) abanikwe uxanduva lokusinceda
nokusebenzisana nathi. Umbulelo wethu ongazenzisiyo kuNksk.
Jane Moleleki, Nksk. NerineJeaven kunye nomabhalane weWCCC, uMnu Clement Williams.
Ngoncedo lwe-DCAS, ikomiti yoPhando noHlahlelo iyile iprojekti yesithuba esiphakathi engamatile-tile
esicatshuwa ekufuneka singeniswe kusetyenziswa iintlobo-ntlobo zoluncwadi ezahlukeneyo.
ISebe
ligunyazisa iBaxter Theatre kunye neMagnet Theatre ukuba ziphuhlise isicatshulwa, idrama eyamkelwa
kakhulu engokuthi kukuthini ukuba yindoda elungileyo kwilizwe lanamhlannje.
Umboniso wenziwa
eBaxter nakwezinye iindawo. Umdlalo ucela umngeni kubabukeli ukuba bacinge ngokufanelekileyo
malunga ngemiba eyahlukeneyo ebalulekileyo nokuqwalasela ngokutsha izigwebo ababenazo.
Emva kokutyelela amaziko enkcubeko asixhenxe aphantsi kwe-WCCC, ikomiti yamaZiko eNkcubeko
iqaphele ukuba amaziko asemaphandleni (eKoekenaap naseSchoemanspoort) awasetyenziswa
ngokupheleleyo.
Kuye ke kwabanjwa ucweyo kunye nabahlali abakwiingingqi ezingqongileyo
ukuvuselela umdla wabo nokuqokelela izimvo zabo malunga kungenziwa njani na ukuba la maziko
asetyenziswe ngokupheleleyo.
Ngaphezulu, unxibelelwano luncedile ukulungiselela ulwakhiwo lobudlelwane nokuqondana phakathi kweKomishini kunye noluntu esebenza kulo.
Amanye amabhunga enkcubeko abhalisiweyo awenze izicelo zenkxaso-mali afumane inkxaso yemali
yokuququzelela imisitho neenkomfa.
Amalungu amathathu eKomishini arhoxile, ngenxa yoko kufuneka
ukuba sisebenze ngabantu abambalwa.
Ndivakalisa umbulelo weKomishini kuGq. Ivan Meyer, okhwelo alihlabileyo lokuba ikomishini idale
inkcubeko efudumeleyo eNtshona Koloni liyinxalenye yenjongo yethu engundoqo .
Ngaphandle kwemingeni esijamelene nayo, iKomishini neSebe zisebenzisene ngokunye njengeqela
elizinikeleyo ekufezekiseni isigunyaziso sethu esinjongo-nye.
