UVAVANYO NGOKUBANZI LOGUNYAZIWE ONIKA INGXELO
Umsebenzi weKomishini yeNkcubeko yeNtshona Koloni kanyaka-mali wama-
2013/14 usekelwephezu kwendlela ekuthaza intatho-nxaxheba ukuqinisekisa
ngokuba amalinge enziwayo ahlala engqalene nemeko-bume eguqu-guqukayo. I-
WCCC izibophelele ekuphuculeni ubonelelo l lweenkonzo kwezobugcisa
nenkcubeko ngokuqinisekis ulwabiwo olupheleleyo nosetyenziso lwezibonelelo
ezikhoyo.
Ngelihambelana nesigunyaziso sayo, i-WCCC inoxanduva lokulawula
ngokwemigangathyo ephakamileyo emiselweyo yaye enziwe afikeleleke kulo lonke
Jane Moleleki
Ukulondolozwa kwala maziko kunye nenkcitho yokusebenza kwa iyidlula lee
ingeniso ayenzayo. Oku kunokubalelwa kwinto yokuba imirhumo ingaphantsi lee kunaleyo ibizwayo
kula maxesha.
Kulo nyaka uphantsi kophengululo, kubanjwe iiseshoni zentsebenziswano noluntu lwasemaphandleni
ngelokufumana iindlela eziqinisekisa ngento yokuba amaziko asetyenziswa ngokupheleleyo.
Enye iseshoni yonxibelelwano yababanjwa kunye neenkokeli zemveli/ zenkcubeko ukuphucula ubudlelwane
nabo babalulekileyo kubuhlakani bentsebenizswano achaphazelekayo ukuphakamisa ukugcinwa,
ukukhuthazwa nokuphuhliswa kwenkcubeko ephondweni eli
Kunyaka-mali ka-2013/14, amabhunga oluntu enkcubeko asixhenxe afumene inkxaso-mali kwi-WCCC
ukuze axhase ngemali iiprojekti zawo, iinkomfa nophando-lwazi.
Ngenxa yokokuba izibophelele ekwandiseni ubandakanyo lwentlalo, iWCCC ithe rhoqo ivavanya ngokutsha imigaqo-nkqubo yayo nendlela yayo yokusebenza.
Umngeni kule meko ngowokuba
akukho malungu eKomishini amele izithili iCentral Karoo, iOverstrandor neWest Coast. Uninzi
lwamalungu luhlala kwisithili seSixeko somasipala waseKapa.
I-DCAS ayiqinisekanga ngokunjalo ngento
yokuba amalungu eWCCC amele ngokwaneleyo umdla wabemi bengingqi yawo.
Nangona kukho le mingeni, iKomishini izimisele ukunikezela ngeenkonzo ezifanelekileyo
nokuhlangabezana neemfuno namabango oluntu kwiNtshona Koloni.
