Imicimbi yenkcubeko:
I-WCCC isebenza ngokusondeleleneyo neSebe lezoBgcisa neNkcubeko
lesizwe namasebe anxulumeneyo karhulumente ngokubhekiselele
nemvumelwano yezobugcisa, inkcubeko nemicimbi yelifa lemveli.
I-WCCC kufuneka yamkele ze iphumeze imgaqo-nkqubo ukukhuthaza nokugcina
intlalo-ntle yabantu beNtshona Koloni, kubandakanywa imigaqo-nkqubo ejolise
ekufezekiseni:
inkuthazo yentlonipho yamalungelo enkcubeko, enkolo nolwimi loluntu
kwiNtshona Koloni; kunye
nokhuselo nokulondolozwa kwembali yendalo, imbali yenkcubeko, ilifa
I-WCCC iqinisekisa ukuba i-DCAS inikezela ngeemfuno zezenkcubeko yoluntu
eNtshona Koloni ngokomthetho.
Amagosa eSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo kufuneka athobele zibonelelo
zecandelo 195, elinika inkcazelo yeempawu zentsulungeko zedemokhrasi
neenqobo ezisesikweni nemithetho-siseko elawula ulawulo lukarhulumente.
ICandelo 195(1)(b) ithi makukhuthazwe ukuba izibonelelo nezoqoqosho
mazisetyenziswe ngokufanelekileyo nangokucikizekileyo.
Oku kuthetha into
yokuba iinkqubo ezisunguliweyo kumacandelo karhulumente mazibe neziphumo
ezigqibeleleyo kodwa ngezona ndleko ziphantsi.
