UHLAHLELO LOBUME
UBume bokunikezelwa kwenkonzo
I-WCCC izibophelele kulondolozo, ukukhuthazwa, nokuphuhliswa kobugcisa nenkcubeko eNtshona
Koloni.
Ukufezekiswa oku, iKomishini iqalise ngenkqubo yokuphucula unxibelelwano phakathi kwayo
nemibutho yoluntu ukulungiselela ukuqinisekisa ngonikezelo lwenkonzo efanelekileyo.
Kulo nyaka uphantsi kovavanyo, iKomishini iqalise ngengqwalasela entsha ehambelana
nokuqwalaselwa kwesidingo senkqubo esekwe kuphando ze inxulumanise oku namalinge e-DCAS.
Ubume bangoku ngokubhekiselele kusetyenziso lwamaziko asixhenxe enkcubeko bubonisa into
yokokuba kukho ibango elikhulu loninzi lwamaziko enkcubeko kwisithili somasipala weSixeko saseKapa
ngokubanzi ngeli lixa lawo akwimimandla esemaphandleni engasetyenziswa ngokupheleleyo.
Oku
kufuneka oku kuqwalaselwe kunyaka-mali ka-2014/15. Kwamkelwe izicelo ezingama-23 zobhalio
lwamabhunga amatsha enkcubeko.
Izicelo zaqwalaselwa yi-WCCC kodwa ezi azibanga
nakuqhutyelwa phambili ngenxa youkba uMphathiswa wePhondo wagunyazisa ukuba khe lume
Angama-24 amabhunga enkcubeko abhalisiweyo.
Awona mabhunga maninzi kolu luhlu yamaKhoisan, okuthetha ukuba ezinye iinkcubeko azimelwanga
ngokwaneleyo.
Amabhunga enkcubeko abhalisiweyo anako ukwenza isicelo senkxaso yemali
ukuxhasa iiprojekti zawo, iinkomfa nophando-lwazi.
Ukuza kuthi ga ngoku ambalwa athe abonelelwa
ngoncedo lwemali kuba uninzi lwamabhunga enkcubeko alukhange lwenze sicelo senkxaso-mali kulo
nyaka uphantsi kovavanyo.
I-WCCC iya kuwuqwalasela lo mba kunyaka-mali wama-2014/15.
