ULAWULO LOMNGCIPHEKO
LiGosa eliNika iNgxelo yeKomishini yeNkcubeko yeNtshona Koloni (WCCC) elithwele uxanduva
lokumilisela uLawulo loMngcipheko lweShishini (ERM) ngokuhambelana nesiCwangciso-nkqubo
soLawulo loMngcipheko seCandelo likaRhulumente sikaNondyebo weSizwe (NTPSRMF) kunye noLawulo
loMngcipheko lweCandelo lwamaShishini (D:ERM) kwiSebe leNkulumbuso (DoTP) elinika inkxaso kwiSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo.
Ukuhambelana nesiCwangciso-nkqubo soLawulo loMngcipheko seCandelo likaRhulumente leCandelo
loLawulo-mali leSizwe (NTPSRMF) nokuzinzisa ngakumbi ulawulo lomngcipheko kwiQumrhu eli ,
uRhulumente weNtshona Koloni (WCG) wamkele uMgaqo-nkqubo we-ERM othi thaca iinjongo
ISicwangciso soPhumezo soNyaka se-ERM siqulunqelwe ukulungiselela ukunceda kumgaqo-nkqubo
we-ERM ye-WCG nokufezekisa iinjongo zesiCwangciso soNyaka soPhumezo soLawulo loMgcipheko
weShishini nezinto ezingundoqo zeQumrhu eli. Oku kulinceda iqumrhu ukuba lifezekise iinjongo zalo,
nezalathisi zendlela yokwenziwa komsebenzi engundoqo, ukwandisa uthatyatho lwezigqibo ezazisa
ngomngcipheko, nokwandisa uhambelwano nemithetho efanelekileyo.
Oku kuchaza ngaphezulu
indima noxanduva lwabalawuli nabasebenzi kulawulo oluzinzileyo lomngcipheko kwiqumrhu ze lichaze
umthetho oncedayo, imigangatho, iindlela, izixhobo nezibonelelo ezisetyenziswayo ukufezekisa
isicwangciso se-ERM.
YiKomiti yoLawulo lobuQhinga noMngcipheko eyongamele isistimu yolawulo lwayo yonke inkqubo
yolawulo lwemingcipheko yequmrhu ze inikezele ngeengxelo ezifunekayo kwiGosa eliphendulayo
ngokubhekiselele kumsebenzi..
IKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi ijonga ngeliso lokhozi elizimeleyo
kwinkqubo yequmrhu kwezolawulo lomngcipheko.
IKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi ifumana iingxelo
zenkqubela phambili ye-ERM rhoqo ngekota kunye nemeko yomngcipheko elikuwo iqumrhu kunye
lokhozi..
Uphononongo lweKomiti yoPhicotho-zincwadi lwenkqubo yolawulo lomngcipheko
luhambelana nesiCwangciso soNyaka soPhumezo se-ERM yequmrhu kunye nemingcipheko
IKomiti ejongene nobuqhetseba kunye noLawulo loMngcipheko (Fraud and Risk Management
Committee) (FARMCO)
IQumrhu eli liseke le iKomiti inguFARMCO ijongene nobuqhetseba noLawulo leMngcipheko ukunceda
iGosa eli phendulayo ekwenzeni umsebenzi walo wolawulo lomngcipheko.
Le komiti isebenza
ngemiqathango evunywe liGosa eliphendulayo.
IKomiti le inamalungu eQumrhu eli aziingcali yaye
abambe izikhundla eziphezulu zolawulo.
Imiiqathango esebenza phantsi kwayo ke iKomiti le iyimisele ukuba ihlale kane ngonyaka.
Iintlanganiso ezihleliyo iKomiti kulo nyaka-mali uphengululwayo zimi ngolu hlobo:
