nesicwangciso sokusebenza sonyaka.
Iimvavanyo zomngcipheko ziqhutywa kwinqanaba eliphezulu
labacwangcisi rhoqo ngonyaka ze zihlaziywe rhoqo ngekota.
Kwinqanaba leenkqubo, iimvavanyo
zomngcipheko ziqhutywa rhoqo ngekota ukulungiselela ukuvavanya ngokutsha nokuhlaziya
imingcipheko ekhoyo nokuchonga imingcipheko evelayo.
Imingcipheko ebonakalayo efanelene
zonyango lomngcipheko ziphuhliswe yaye zilawulwa yaye zabiwe ngokwabanini bomngcipheko.
Iirejista zenkqubo yomngcipheko zivunywa ngumlawuli ofanelekileyo wenkqubo.
IFARMCO ejongene nobuqhetseba noMngcipheko iyaqinisekisa, ilubngelelanise ngokokubaleka
kwezinto ze icebise iGosa eliphendulayo ngokuba yeyiphi na imingcipheko ethe yancitshiswa
ngokusabela/ ngonyango lomngcipheko olufanelekileyo ukulungiselela ukuhlangabezana neenjongo
zeqhinga zequmrhu.
Le nkqubo iqhutywa rhoqo ngekota yaye incedisa ngexesha lophengululo
lobume bomsebenzi wequmrhu.
