ubhalisileyo kuluhlu kuqala kuqinisekiswe ukuba i-WCBD4 emdizayo ayindalanga ngaphezu
ICandelo likaNondyebo wePhondo lincedisa amaqumrhu karhulumente ukucutha umngcipheko
wochaphazeleko nalapho kuye kufunyaniswe ukuba kukho abalawuli beenkampani
