Xa bekunofunyaniswa
uchaphazeleko oko bekunokuthathwa njengorhwaphilizo kuLawulo lweeNtengo kwaye, emva
kophando, loo mniki-zinkonzo ebeya kuthathwa njengongafanelekanga.
