nezona mali zonyaka ophelayo, namanqaku, aquka isishwankathelo semigaqo-nkqubo
ebalulekileyo yokunika ingxelo nezinye iinkcukacha ezinika ingcaciso.
Uxanduva lwegosa eliphendulayo lweengxelo-mali
