Onegunya lokunika ingxelo nophendulayo unoxanduva lokwenza amalungiselelo nokubonisa
ngendlela enobulungisa iingxelo zemali ngokweMigangatho yaseMzantsi Afrika yeZenzo
zokuNika iNgxelo eziVunyiweyo Jikelele (iSA Standards of GRAP), okufunekayo ngokomthetho
iPublic Finance Management Act of South Africa, ka-1999 (Umthetho woku-1 ka-1999)
(PFMA) necandelo le-15(6) lomthetho iWestern Cape Cultural Commission and Cultural
