uhlahlo-lwabiwo-mali oluhamba ngokwezicwangciso.
Ukuxhasa inkqubo yohlahlo-lwabiwo-mali yoomasipala ngeziphakamiso
kwiinjongo zentlalo noqoqosho nemigaqo-nkqubo kunye nonxulumaniso
lokubandakanyeka kweKomiti yeNkcitho kaRulumente woMmandla. 3.2.2.4
