kuqfumana inkxaso ngeendlela zokwenza ezimanyanisiweyo kwinkqubo
yocwangciso yeentengo ukudala imeko eza kuyenza ziphinda-phindeke
iziphumo okanye inzuzom kunyuke nomthamo weenkonzo zinganyuswanga
zona iindleko zokwenza oko kusenziwa ngokuthenga kakhulu ngexesha /
12
neekhontrakhthi zorhwebelwano ezikhawulelanayo. 5.
Luza kuqwalaselwa uphuhliso lwabasebenzi be-SCM nabaniki-nkonzo. Uphuhliso
lwabasebenzi kwizakhono ze-SCM nolwazi emazikweni
kuququzelelwa kuqinisekiswe ukuba luyenzeka ngokubanika uqeqesho
longenelelo olungqalileyo, idesika yoncedo, uncedo nesikhokelo, amaphulo
