IMvELA-PHI
ISebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko neMidlalo lizibophelele ekuphuculeni ubomi babantu
ngezobugcisa.
Imbono yethu ikholose ekuvuleni amathuba ngokuququzelela uphuhliso
lwezakhono, ukuchongwa kwetalente, ngokwakha ubudlelane obubalulekileyo,
nokubonelela ngamathuba okwenza ukuba abantu babalasele.
I-DCAS ikholelwa ukuba kufuneka lixhaswe iphuhliso lezobugcisa nenkcubeko eluntwini
ukuze lube lolubonakalayo, olunezibonelelo eziziziseko nezizinzileyo.
Ikwenza oku
ngokwenza ubudlelane noluntu, nangokudala amathuba okuba ubani agqwese koko
akwenzayo.
Imidlalo eboniswe apha namhlanje bubungqina bempumelelo yenkqubo ye-DCAS
yobugcisa nenkcubeko.
Apha sibona iziqhamo zoququzelelo olusebenzayo lweenzame
zoompondo zihlanjiwe kule nkalo, uluntu, umasipala kwakunye nethiyetha ezikudidii
oluphezulu.
I-DCAS iqinisekisa ukuba ukuphuhliswa komdlalo weqonga eCape Winelands ne-
Eden kuqhubela phambili. Ikwenza oku ngokunceda abo babalaseleyo ukuba badlale
kumaqonga aphezulu ase-Artscape, eBaxter Theatre nakwiKlein Karoo Nasionale Kunstefees (KKNK).
Yonwabela ubugcisa betalente besithili saseCape Winelands nase-Eden.
