Ithala leencwadi lasePaarl latshintshelwa
Ithala leencwadi elipheleleyo elinemisebenzi emibini eMzantsi Afrika, ithala
leencwadi loluntu lesikolo samabanga aphantsi iKlapmuts lavulwa ngomhla we-18
14 kweyeThupha ngo-2011.
Ingcinga yokudibanisa ithala leencwadi lesikolo kunye
nethala leencwadi loluntu laqala ukuphakanyiswa yinqununu yesikolo samabanga
aphantsi iKlapmuts laza iphupha lakhe lazalisekiswa kuluntu olunemingeni yemeko
Ithala leencwadi lesikolo linceda abafundi aba-1,326 besikolo
samabanga aphantsi iKlapmust, kodwa likwasebenza njengeziko lezixhobo
ekufumaneka i-intanethi simahla kubemi abangama- 9,000 baseKlapmuts.
Umzekelo wethala elinemisebenzi emibini ufumana ingqwalasela engaphezulu njalo
kwisizwe naphesheya kolwandle kwaye lo mzekelo wempumelelo wethala leencwadi
elinemisebenzi emibini lingalinganiswa kwenye indawo.
