lineendawo zokusebenzela zekhompyutha ezingama-20 ezibonelela nge-intanethi
esimahla ngothungelwano oluyi -Smartcape inani elikhulu lezi zikhululo
zokusebenzela lifumaneka nakweliphina ithala leencwadi loluntu eNtshona Koloni.
Likwanayo neholo yokufundela, indawo yokuhlala yolutsha,
amagumbi eentlanganiso negumbi lemidlalo elinesixhasi somashini bokudlala iWii gaming.
