Umsebenzi obalulekileyo weWCLS kukubonelela ngemathiriyeli kumathala eencwadi
oluntu aphantsi kwayo.
Umsebenzi wenziwa phantsi kolawulo oluyintloko
lokukhetha, ukufumana, uluhlu nokwenziwa kwemathiriyeli eyabelwa amathala
kawonke-wonke ngendlela edlula kuthungelwano lwamathala ommandla.
IQumrhu eliseMbindini linomthwalo wokukhetha, ukufumana ukucwangcisa, ukulungisa
ngobuchule nokulungisa imathiriyeli yethala leencwadi, ulawulo lwendlela yethala
leencwadi yokusebenza kwekhompyutha, ulawulo neenkonzo zenkxaso ngokunjalo
nenkonzo yongqinisiso, uphando, upapasho nokwazisa.
IQumrhu eliseMbindini
lineeyunithi ezintathu, ezizezi; uKhetho nokuFumana, iiNkonzo yobuGcisa
neeNkonzo Jikelele.
Ukukhetha nokuFumana imathiriyeli
27 KwiCandelo loKhetho umsebenzi ukwiindawo zolawulo eziyintloko ezimbini, ezizezi
uhlolo, ukhetho nokufumana imathiriyeli yethala leencwadi.
