yeBrocade)
ISLIMS yaphunyezwa kumaziko amathala angama- 72 koomasipala abali- 13
basemaphandleni.
kwiSLIMS ngenxa yocimo olwalukufuphi ekupheleni kweyeNkanga ngo- 2011.
Into
ephambili yayikukufudusa amathala eencwadi ajikelezisa iPALS kuSLIMS.
ICandelo leKhompyutha laba nakho ngokunjalo ukufudusa amanye amathala eencwadi
asebenza ngezandla ngeli xesha lale nkqubo.
Le nkqubo yenza ukuba amathala
eencwadi akoomasipala abe kwinkqubo enye yolawulo.
Ukuphunyezwa kweSLIMS kumathala eencwadi kawonke-wonke emaphandleni uya
kuqhutywa kunyaka-mali ozayo.
ICandelo lokukhathaloga
Owona msebenzi ungundoqo weCandelo lokuKhathaloga kukwenza uluhlu
olufumaneka nge-intanethi kwiSLIMS.
Kule meko ibizwa ngokuba yi-enjini
yeNkonzo yeThala leencwadi.
Kuyimfuneko kubasebenzi ukuba balayishe ulwazi
ngokuchanekileyo kangangoko ukuze baqinisekise ukufunyanwa kwakhona kolwazi
ngabasebenzisi bethala leencwadi.
Ukwenziwa okokuqala koluhlu lweencwadi
zeentsomi kuyenziwa njengoko kukhawuleza ukufaka izihloko zeentsomi kwiSLIMS
kunokudawunlowuda kwi WorldCat.
Ukukhutshelwa koluhlu lwezihloko ezingezo ntsomi kwenziwa kwiWorld Cat.
Imveliso yeCandelo lokuKhathaloga yachaphazeleka ngokugxekekayo
kukutshintshelwa kuPALS ukuya kuSLIMS ngomhla wo-1kweyoMdumba 2011.
Kukho izizathu ezahlukeneyo zoku: 31
ithala leencwadi ngalinye libe noluhlu lwalo olwenziweyo njengakuPALS
kubekho ngoku uluhlu olunye kwiSLIMS, Kukho kuphela uluhlu olunye kwi
SLIMS
Njengokuba olunye uluhlu luka PALS luqulathe idatha efakwe kakubi okanye
engangqinelaniyo, yonke ngoku idityaniswe kuluhlu olunye lweSLIMS.
Nangona abanye abenzi boluhlu babeqhubekeka besenza imisebenzi yabo
