esetyenziweyo Inkonzo ngokuPhangaleleyo
Eyona njongo nento ekujoliswe kuyo yiNkonzo ngokuPhangaleleyo kukubonelela
ngenkxaso kumacandelo angaphakathi, abasebenzi, amathala eencwadi emimandla
kunye namathala eencwadi oluntu.
INkonzo ngokuPhangaleleyo iquka amacandelo
amahlanu, angala; iNkxaso ngokuPhangaleleyo, iziNgqinisiso eziseMbindini (SN),
uPapasho, uKwazisa noPhando.
Candelo leNkxaso ngokuPhangaleleyo
ICandelo leNkxaso ngokuPhangaleleyo linomthwalo wezinto zonke zabasebenzi
nemicimbi emalunga nabasebenzi beNkonzo yeNtshona Koloni yeThala leencwadi.
Lisebenza njengabalungelelanisi phakathi kweNkonzo yeThala leencwadi kunye
neSebe leMicimbi yeNkcubeko nemiDlalo.
Ngaphezulu, libonelela abaphathi kunye
nabasebenzi ngolwazi lwemihla yonke malunga nepolisi yabasebenzi.
Bafundisa
abasebenzi malunga nenkonzo yoncedo nemicimbi enxulumene nomsebenzi.
Bakwancedisa abasebenzi ekuzaliseni ifomu, njengezezindlu/imali evunyelweyo
yokuqesha, ikhefu, intshukumo zogwayimbo, inkxaso yempilo, ukuphela
komsebenzi, izicelo zesambuku sokuyeka ukufumana ukuxhamla umhlala phantsi.
