Icandelo 49(2) loMthetho iNational Heritage Resources Act, uMthetho 25 ka-1999, unika uMphathiswa weMicimbi
yeNkcubeko kwiPhondo leNtshona Koloni igunya lokumisela inkundla ezimeleyo eneengcali ezintathu eziza
kuqwalasela izibheno.
Inkundla kaMphathiswa iza kuva izibheno ngezigqibo ezithathwe liBhunga leLifa leMveli
leNtshona Koloni (HWC) ezithunyelwe kuyo nguMphathiswa.
Inkundla kaMphathiswa ekhankanywe kwicandelwana (2), ekuqwalaseleni kwayo izibheno ezithunyelwe kuyo
nguMphathsiwa, kufuneka inike ingqalelo kwezi zinto:
ukubaluleka kwezibonelelo zelifa lemveli ezichaphazelekayo kwimiba yenkcubeko;
imithetho-siseko yolondolozo lwelifa lemveli; kananjalo
nawuphi na omnye umba ochaphazelekayo oziswe phambi kwayo ngulowo ufake isibheno okanye ngugunyaziwe wezibonelelo zelifa lemveli.
Ukuze babhaliswe kulo vimba wesebe, abagqatswa kufuneka babe nolwazi namava aphangaleleyo kwelinye lala
makhondo alandelayo nangaphezulu, phakathi kwezinye izinto, umthetho, inkcubeko, i-akhiyoloji, ipaliyontoloji,
ubuchule bokudizayina nokwakha, ulondolozo lwezolwakhiwo (kubandakanywa ezenkcubeko), ulondolozo lwendalo,
ulondolozo lwee-obhjekthi, ucwangciso lwedolophu kunye nokuyilwa kweedolophu.
