3 IMISEBENZI YESEBE LOKHUSELEKO LOLUNTU  ICANDELO 14(1)(A)
ISebe loKhuseleko loLuntu liphumeza isigunyaziso somgaqo-siseko nomthetho
sokbeka esweni zonke ii-arhente zonyanzeliso lomthetho, kwanokuphumeza
imigaqo-nkqubo yokhuseleko nokhuselo.
ISebe lijongene nokulawula imisebenzi
yonke yezokhuseleko oko likwenza egameni lazo zonke iiNtloko zamaSebe
kuRhulumente weNtshona Koloni kunye nokubonelela ngeenkonzo zenkxaso
leKomiti eLawulayo (MEC), iNtloko yeSebe kunye
nemisebenzi phakathi esebeni.
3.1 INKQUBO 1: INKXASO YEZOLAWULO
3.1.1 Ukubonelela ngeenkonzo zenkxaso yobuchule bokusebenza nolawulo ku-
MEC, iNtloko yesebe, imisebenzi yeSebe kunye namanye amaqumrhu
achaphazelekayo. Iinjongo zenkqubo kukunika igalelo elinemfezeko kwii-
Ofisi ze-MEC neNtloko yeSebe ukuze bona babe ziinkokeli ezinobuchule
kananjalo baqinisekise ulawulo norhulumento olufezekileyo.
3.1.2 Le misebenzi ilandelayo yenziwa ngokwale Nkqubo:
Ukuqinisekisa ukuba isebe liyayithobela imigaqo ephathelene nezimali
ngokubonelela ulawulo lwezimali neenkonzo zeengcebiso; kunye
Nokuqinisekisa ukusebenza ngobuchule nangemfezeko kwesebe
ngokulandela isicwangciso-qhinga, ulawulo lokusebenza kwenkqubo,
ezonxibelelwano nenkxaso yezolawulo.
3.2 INKQUBO 2 NEYE-3: UNOBHALA WEZOKHUSELO NOKHUSELEKO
3.2.1 Ukubeka esweni indlela yokuziphatha, ubuchule bokusebenza nokusebenza
Ukuqinisekisa ukufezekiswa kweSigunyaziso
soMgaqo-siseko esinikwe amaphondo esiphathelene nokukhuthaza ubudlelane obulungileyo
phakathi kwabahlali namapolisa, oko ekwenza ngenkqubo egxininisa
ukuchaphazeleka uluntu luphela nokuqinisekisa ukuba zonke izikhalazo
ngenkonzo yesipolisa ePhondweni
iqwalaselwa
ngokungenasheyi
nangobuchule.
3.2.2 Le misebenzi ilandelayo yenziwa ngokwale Nkqubo:
Ukuqhuba uphando ukuze kwaziswe amahlakani entsebenziswano,
ukuba neempembelelo kulwabiwo lwemithombo okanye izibonelelo
kwiPhondo, kunye nokunika igalelo kuqulunqo lwemigaqo-nkqubo
echaphazelekayo Ukongamela ezokupolisa ePhondweni
ukubanceda ukuba ukukhawulelana nezinto ezibaxhalabisayo
ezimalunga nokhuseleko kunye neemfuno jikelele zabahlali bendawo.
Ukukhuthaza ubudlelane nentsebenziswano phakathi kwenkonzo
yokupolisa nabahlali ngokumisela nokumenteyina IiForam zamaPolisa asekuHlaleni
eNatyisiweyo i-Expanded Partnership Programme (EPP)
Ukunabisa ukhuseleko ngobambiswano oluzinzileyo nemibutho
